20rumours%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20called%20the%20Kathua%20attack%20a%20%26quot%3Bfresh%20infiltration%26quot%3B%20and%20pointed%20at%20Pakistan%20without%20naming%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20our%20hostile%20neighbour%20who%20always%20tries%20to%20damage%20the%20peaceful%20environment%20in%20our%20country.%20This%20(Hiranagar%20Terror%20attack)%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20fresh%20infiltration%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20earlier%2C%20a%20bus%20on%20its%20way%20to%20the%20Shiv%20Khori%20cave%20temple%20came%20under%20attack%20in%20Reasi.%20The%20terrorists%20opened%20fire%20after%20the%20bus%20driver%20refused%20to%20deboard%20the%20passengers%2C%20but%20lost%20control%20and%20fell%20into%20the%20gorge%2C%20the%20bus%20company's%20manager%20said.%20Nine%20people%20were%20killed%20and%2033%20injured%20in%20the%20incident.%20The%20attack%20was%20carried%20out%20on%20the%20directions%20of%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20commander%20Abu%20Hamza%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718160240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fm9p284uo_doda-terror-attack_625x300_12_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterrorists-attack-army-post-in-j-ks-doda-3rd-terror-incident-in-3-days-5871011%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20encounter%20is%20on%20between%20terrorists%20and%20security%20forces%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Doda%20after%20they%20attacked%20an%20army%20base%20late%20last%20night%2C%20said%20police.%20Five%20soldiers%20and%20a%20special%20police%20officer%20(SPO)%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20shootout.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterrorists-attack-army-post-in-j-ks-doda-3rd-terror-incident-in-3-days-5871011%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterrorists-attac