2%26quot%3BBJP%20Had%20To%20Face%20Defeat%26quot%3B%3A%20Sharad%20Pawar%20On%20Ayodhya%20Result%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENCP%20(SP)%20leader%20Sharad%20Pawar%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20the%20people%20of%20Ayodhya%20have%20demonstrated%20how%20to%20correct%20the%20%26quot%3Bpolitics%20of%20temple%26quot%3B%20by%20defeating%20the%20BJP's%20candidate%20in%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20town%20in%20recent%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20a%20traders'%20meet%20in%20Baramati%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20highlighted%20that%20while%20the%20BJP%20had%20secured%20more%20than%20300%20seats%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20this%20time%20their%20count%20dropped%20to%20240%2C%20well%20short%20of%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20result%20shows%20that%20their%2060%20seats%20got%20reduced%2C%20and%20in%20this%20reduction%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20is%20a%20key%20state%20as%20the%20people%20there%20gave%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20verdict%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pawar%20said%20he%20had%20anticipated%20that%20Ram%20temple%20would%20be%20the%20election%20agenda%20and%20the%20ruling%20party%20would%20get%20votes%2C%20but%20the%20people%20of%20our%20country%20are%20quite%20wise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20they%20realised%20that%20votes%20were%20being%20sought%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20different%20stand%20and%20the%20BJP%20had%20to%20face%20defeat%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20veteran%20politician%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20major%20upset%20in%20the%20Faizabad%20parliamentary%20constituency%2C%20where%20the%20temple%20town%20of%20Ayodhya%20is%20situated%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20candidate%20Awadhesh%20Prasad%20defeated%20sitting%20BJP%20MP%20Lallu%20Singh%20by%20a%20margin%20of%2054%2C567%20votes%20in%20recent%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pawar%2C%20a%20key%20member%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20said%20the%20Opposition%20was%20apprehensive%20about%20the%20temple%20being%2