ore-fed-outcome-support-at-2-277-124061200056_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThe%20Truth%20Is...%26quot%3B%3A%20Federer%20Debunks%20'Effortless'%20Myth%20In%20College%20Speech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETennis%20legend%20Roger%20Federer%20gave%20inspiring%20life%20lessons%20to%20students%20at%20the%20Dartmouth%20College%20after%20the%2020-time%20Grand%20Slam%20champion%20received%20an%20honourary%20doctorate%20in%20Humane%20Letters%20on%20Sunday.%20While%20addressing%20the%20Class%20of%202024%2C%20the%20Swiss%20maestro%20revealed%20that%20this%20was%20only%20the%20second%20time%20he%20was%20setting%20foot%20on%20a%20college%20campus.%20Federer%20shared%20three%20key%20life%20lessons%20with%20the%20students%20in%20his%20'unforgettable'%20speech%2C%20which%20last%20nearly%2025%20minutes%20at%20the%20Dartmouth%20College%20in%20in%20Hanover%2C%20New%20Hampshire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2042-year-old%20insisted%20that%20the%20word%20%26quot%3Beffortless%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20myth%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20had%20to%20work%20hard%20for%20everything%20he%20achieved%20in%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20say%20that%20as%20someone%20who%20has%20heard%20that%20word%20a%20lot.%20'Effortless.'%20People%20would%20say%20my%20play%20was%20effortless.%20Most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20they%20meant%20it%20as%20a%20compliment...%20But%20it%20used%20to%20frustrate%20me%20when%20they%20would%20say.%20'He%20barely%20broke%20a%20sweat!'.%20The%20truth%20is%2C%20I%20had%20to%20work%20very%20hard...%20to%20make%20it%20look%20easy.%20I%20spent%20years%20whining...%20swearing...%20throwing%20my%20racket...%20before%20I%20learned%20to%20keep%20my%20cool...%20I%20didn't%20get%20where%20I%20got%20on%20pure%20talent%20alone.%20I%20got%20there%20by%20trying%20to%20outwork%20my%20opponents%2C%26quot%3B%20Federer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ERoger%20Federer's%20Commencement%20Address%20at%20Dartmouth%20yesterday%20might%20be%20the%20best%20speech%20he's%20ever%20given.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAmazingly%20articulate%2C%20funny%2C%20full%20of%20wisdom.%20Made%20me%20laugh%20and%20tear%20up.%20I'm%20so%20very%20proud%20to%20have%20had%20him%20as%20my%20idol%20for%20the%20past%20two%20decades.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIf%20you%20have%2025%20minutes%20to%20spare...%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fqfd9io9kzV%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fqfd9io9kzV%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Bastien%20Fachan%20(%40BastienFachan)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBastienFachan%2Fstatus%2F1800125126035362194%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2010%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20second%20life%20lesson%2C%20Federer%20recalled%20his%20loss%20to%20longtime%20rival%20and%20friend%20Rafael%20Nadal%20in%20the%20final%20of%20Wimbledon%20in%202008%2C%20adding%20that%20'it's%20only%20a%20point'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20work%20harder%20than%20you%20thought%20possible...%20and%20still%20lose.%20I%20have.%20I%20lost%20Wimbledon.%20I%20lost%20my%20number-one%20ranking.%20And%20suddenly%2C%20people%20said%2C%20'He%20had%20a%20great%20run.%20Is%20this%20the%20changing%20of%20the%20guard%3F'%20But%20I%20knew%20what%20I%20had%20to%20do...%20keep%20working.%20And%20keep%20competing%2C%26quot%3B%20Federer%20added%20while%20emphasising%20that%20'life%20is%20bigger%20than%20the%20court'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFederer%2C%20who%20turned%20pro%20in%201998%2C%20retired%20from%20the%20sport%20in%202022.%20He%20played%20his%20final%20game%2C%20a%20doubles%20match%20with%20Nadal%2C%20at%20the%20Laver%20Cup%2C%20which%20was%20won%20by%20Team%20USA's%20Jack%20Sock%20and%20Frances%20Tiafoe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Federer%20and%20Nadal%20were%20seen%20crying%20after%20the%20latter's%20farewell%20match%20ended%20in%20a%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718154240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2