ree%20adjudged%20Yousef%20Aymen's%2073rd-minute%20equaliser%20as%20fair%20after%20the%20ball%20appeared%20to%20have%20gone%20out%20of%20play.%20The%20controversial%20decision%20turned%20the%20game%20on%20its%20head%20as%20Qatar%20scored%20their%20second%20through%20Ahmed%20Al-Rawi%20in%20the%2085th%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20after%20the%20Indians%20came%20within%20touching%20distance%20of%20scripting%20history%20after%20going%201-0%20at%20half%20time%2C%20with%20Kuwait%20and%20Afghanistan%20goalless%20in%20the%20day's%20other%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Indian%20dream%20lay%20shattered%20in%20a%20space%20of%20few%20minutes%20in%20the%20second%20half%20courtesy%20the%20controversial%20goal%20by%20Aymen%20and%20the%20ensuing%20strike%20by%20Al-Rawi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWe'll%20leave%20it%20here!%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FINDQAT%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23INDQAT%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FIndianFootball%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23IndianFootball%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5KhtyOfrvS%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F5KhtyOfrvS%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20FanCode%20(%40FanCode)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFanCode%2Fstatus%2F1800595521628999862%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2011%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Eid%20Al-Rashidi%20struck%20the%20winner%20for%20Kuwait%20in%20the%2081st%20minute.%20Qatar%20and%20Kuwait%20thus%20progressed%20to%20the%20second%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20playing%20barely%20five%20days%20after%20the%20international%20retirement%20of%20arguably%20the%20country's%20greatest%20footballer%20Sunil%20Chhetri%2C%20not%20many%20gave%20the%20beleaguered%20121-ranked%20India%20side%20a%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Igor%20Stimac's%20wards%20turned%20the%20tables%20in%20style%20and%20looked%20on%20course%20after%20Chhangte's%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChhangte%2C%20the%2027-year-old%20winger%20from%20Mizoram's%20Lunglei%2C%20struck%20the%20ball%20accurately%20into%20the%20bottom%20corner%20after%20a%20diagonal%20pass%20from%20Brandon%20Fernandes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20received%20the%20ball%2C%20he%20made%20no%20mistake%20in%20outsmarting%20his%20marker%20and%20broke%20the%20deadlock%20to%20silence%20the%20backers%20of%20the%20fancied%20hosts%20at%20the%20Jassim%20Bin%20Hamad%20Stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20redemption%20of%20sorts%20for%20Chhangte%20as%20he%20found%20the%20back%20of%20the%20net%20after%20failing%20to%20convert%20two%20chances%20created%20by%20Brandon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20also%20made%20Chhangte%20India's%20highest-scoring%20active%20player%20with%20eight%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20good%20number%20of%20Indian%20supporters%20also%20made%20their%20way%20into%20the%20venue%20and%20at%20times%20outperformed%20the%20home%20crowd%20when%20it%20came%20to%20cheering%20after%20Chhangte's%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20weathering%20an%20initial%20wave%20of%20attacks%20from%20Qatar%20when%20the%20day's%20skipper%20and%20goalkeeper%20Gurpreet%20Singh%20Sandhu%20pulled%20off%20a%20couple%20of%20crucial%20saves%2C%20India%2C%20without%20Chhetri%20after%20many%20years%2C%20began%20to%20put%20pressure%20on%20their%20hosts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMehtab%20Singh%20also%20played%20his%20part%2C%20making%20a%20goal-line%20block%20off%20a%20shot%20by%20Ahmed%20Alrawi%2C%20to%20keep%20India%20in%20the%20hunt%20early%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20first%20half%20wore%20on%2C%20India's%20three%20forwards%2C%20Rahim%20Ali%2C%20Chhangte%2C%20and%20Manvir%20Singh%2C%20along%20with%20midfielders%20Fernandes%2C%20Jeakson%20Singh%2C%20and%20Suresh%20Wangjam%20formed%20a%20six-man%20press%20that%20launched%20attacks%20in%20waves%20and%20did%20not%20allow%20the%20Qatar%20defenders%20to%20settle%20on%20the%20ball%20in%20their%20own%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJeakson%20played%20Rahim%20through%20behind%20the%20Qatar%20defence%20in%20the%2025th%20minute%2C%20and%20the%20latter%20sprinted%20into%20the%20box%20and%20drove%20it%20hard%20and%20low%20across%20the%20goal%2C%20but%20the%20cross%20evaded%20the%20onrushing%20Chhangte%20and%20Manvir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20immediately%2C%20Manvir%20was%20played%20through%20in%20the%2031st%20minute%20and%20just%20had%20the%20keeper%20to%20beat%2C%20but%20his%20effort%20was%20parried%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChhangte%20intercepted%20a%20pass%20in%20the%20Qatar%20third%2C%20played%20a%20one-two%20with%20Brandon%20and%20squared%20it%20to%20Rahim%2C%20who%20was%20just%20a%20yard%20short%20of%20the%20pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Qatar%20defence%20looked%20shaken%20and%20the%20Indians%20were%20there%20to%20capitalise%20on%20it.%20Chhangte%20opened%20the%20scoring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJay%20Gupta%2C%20after%20a%20one-two%20with%20Jeakson%20on%20the%20left%20flank%2C%20played%20it%20back%20to%20Brandon%2C%20who%20found%20the%20perfect%20weight%20on%20his%20through%20pass%20to%20Chhangte.%20The%20nifty%20winger%20coolly%20finished%20it%20at%20the%20near%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20momentum%20completely%20changed%20in%20the%20second%20half.%20India%20were%20no%20longer%20employing%20their%20six-man%20press%20as%20they%20remained%20content%20with%20a%20mid-block%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQatar%20were%20looking%20to%20work%20the%20half-space%20channels%2C%20and%20Alrawi%2C%20the%20recipient%20of%20a%20second%20cut-back%20had%20his%20shot%20blocked%20again%20by%20Mehtab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESahal%20Abdul%20Samad%20and%20Liston%20Colaco%2C%20who%20had%20replaced%20Fernandes%20and%20Rahim%2C%20almost%20created%20that%20chance.%20Prowling%20on%20the%20counter%2C%20Sahal%20jinked%20past%20his%20marker%20and%20set%20Liston%20through%2C%20but%20the%20latter%20was%20just%20inches%20offside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQatar%20struck%20back%20with%20a%20little%20over%2015%20minutes%20of%20regulation%20time%20left%2C%20as%20Ayman%20turned%20in%20a%20cut-back%20from%20point-blank%20range.%20The%20Indian%20players%20vehemently%20protested%20the%20decision%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20ball%20had%20already%20gone%20out%20of%20play%20before%20the%20goal%20was%20scored%2C%20but%20the%20referee%20did%20not%20budge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJay%20caused%20some%20stir%20down%20the%20left%20in%20the%2082nd%2C%20but%20a%20poor%20touch%20meant%20that%20the%20Qatar%20keeper%20stepped%20out%20and%20parried%20it%20off%20his%20feet.%20Liston%20had%20a%20chance%20to%20score%20from%20the%20rebound%2C%20but%20his%20shot%20was%20deflected%20before%20being%20collected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlrawi%20broke%20Indian%20hearts%20again%20when%20he%20curled%20it%20from%20outside%20the%20box%20and%20into%20the%20bottom%20corner%20past%20a%20flailing%20Gurpreet.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718153400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fqnorldj_qatar-goal_625x300_12_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Findia-robbed-of-chance-to-script-history-lose-1-2-to-qatar-5869880%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20controversial%20decision%20turned%20the%20game%20on%20its%20head%20as%20Qatar%20scored%20their%20second%20through%20Ahmed%20Al-Rawi%20in%20the%2085th%20minute.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Findia-robbed-of-chance-to-script-history-lose-1-2-to-qatar-5869880%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Findia-robbed-of-chance-to-script-history-lose-1-2-to-qatar-5869880%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Findia-robbed-of-chance-to-script-history-lose-1-2-to