stice-2426021%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecently%20won%20an%20appeal%20%3C%2Fa%3Eregarding%20the%20photograph%20in%20a%20Luxembourg%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECara%20gained%20over%20600%2C000%20users%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20June%20and%20has%20moved%20to%20the%20top%20of%20App%20Store%20rankings%2C%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eaccording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2024%2F06%2F06%2Fa-social-app-for-creatives-cara-grew-from-40k-to-650k-users-in-a-week-because-artists-are-fed-up-with-metas-ai-policies%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETechCrunch%20report%20last%20week.%20%3C%2Fa%3EThe%20app's%20spike%20in%20sign-ups%20came%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-instagram-facebook-photos-used-in-ai-models-training-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20after%20Meta's%20chief%20product%20officer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Chris%20Cox%2C%20said%20last%20month%20that%20the%20company%20uses%20publicly%20available%20photos%20and%20text%20from%20Instagram%20and%20Facebook%20to%20train%20Emu%2C%20and%20after%20European%20users%20were%20notified%20that%20their%20posts%20will%20be%20used%20to%20train%20AI%2C%20unless%20they%20opt%20out%2C%20in%20late%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArtists%20who%20are%20choosing%20to%20leave%20for%20Cara%20are%20doing%20it%20out%20of%20outrage%20and%20disagreement%26quot%3B%20with%20Meta's%20AI%20policy%2C%20said%20Meridian%20Culpepper%2C%20an%20animation%20artist%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22751a7f68-5032-4238-9443-d6442bfa6d4d%5C%22%3ELosing%20hard-earned%20followings%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EProfessional%20artists%20said%20they%20have%20issues%20with%20Instagram%20beyond%20AI%2C%20including%20that%20they%20feel%20forced%20to%20buy%20ads%20to%20be%20seen.%20But%20giving%20up%20the%20platform%20completely%20won't%20be%20easy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstagram%20has%20been%20important%20to%20me%20as%20an%20artist%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20how%20I%20started%20my%20art%20career%2C%26quot%3B%20Kent%2C%20who%20has%20nearly%2075%2C000%20followers%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20it%20allowed%20her%20to%20connect%20with%20art%20collectors%20from%20around%20the%20world%20and%20helped%20her%20transition%20to%20painting%20full-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKent%20said%20she%20doesn't%20like%20how%20Meta%20is%20taking%20artists'%20creative%20work%20and%20profiting%20from%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20these%20concerns%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20have%20to%20keep%20my%20Instagram%20for%20now%2C%20since%20that%20is%20where%20my%20collectors%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20Kent%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECulpepper%2C%20the%20Los%20Angeles-based%20animation%20artist%2C%20said%20she's%20sticking%20around%20because%20tech%20giants%20like%20Meta%20set%20an%20example%20for%20others%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20staying%20on%20Instagram%20because%20I%20see%20the%20value%20in%20fighting%20for%20that%20choice%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Culpepper.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20going%20to%20delete%20my%20account%20and%20run%20away.%20I%20want%20to%20stay%20and%20see%20the%20issue%20resolved.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22880a24be-c4de-411d-bcab-92337c1f521a%5C%22%3ENot%20just%20an%20artist's%20problem%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOpting%20out%20can%20be%20a%20hassle.%20Meta%20asks%20users%20to%20go%20through%20several%20steps%20and%20fill%20out%20a%20form%20that%20asks%20them%20to%20provide%20proof%20that%20their%20private%20photos%20or%20personal%20details%20show%20up%20in%20Meta's%20AI%20model%2C%20along%20with%20the%20relevant%20prompts%20used%20to%20get%20the%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20filling%20out%20the%20form%20and%20providing%20%26quot%3Bevidence%26quot%3B%20is%20not%20a%20guarantee%20that%20accounts%20will%20be%20excluded%20from%20scraping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20automatically%20fulfill%20requests%20sent%20using%20this%20form.%20We%20review%20them%20consistent%20with%20your%20local%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20text%20above%20the%20form%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221788%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Meta%20AI%20scraper%20%26quot%3Bproof%26quot%3B%20form%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6668076ded9a404d829c5171%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221168%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMeta's%20form%20asks%20users%20for%20%26quot%3Bevidence%26quot%3B%20that%20their%20personal%20information%20is%20being%20scraped.%3Cp%3EFacebook%20screenshot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20artists%20said%20governments%20should%20give%20users%20the%20right%20to%20opt%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20also%20quite%20upset%20that%20Singapore%20doesn't%20have%20the%20option%20for%20people%20here%20to%20opt%20out%20of%20Instagram%20and%20Facebook%20using%20our%20pictures%20and%20artworks%20for%20their%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Noah%20Smith%2C%20a%20Singapore-based%20animation%20student%20who%20said%20he%20is%20on%20Instagram%20and%20Cara.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b133471e-0444-45c8-861f-09fc469d50d7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFar%20from%20perfect%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EArtists%2C%20including%20Kent%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%20said%20they're%20using%20platforms%20like%20Cara%20to%20hedge%20against%20the%20whims%20of%20any%20one%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20past%20few%20years%20have%20shown%20me%20that%20I%20can't%20build%20a%20business%20that%20is%20dependent%20on%20one%20platform.%20Instagram%20can%20take%20my%20audience%20away%20with%20a%20simple%20change%20of%20the%20algorithm%2C%26quot%3B%20Kent%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20opening%20an%20account%20on%20Cara%2C%20she%20has%20also%20started%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-chatbot-says-trained-on-youtube-videos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%20channel%20to%20share%20more%20long-form%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwitching%20platforms%20come