AI%20had%20argued%20in%20a%20court%20filing%20that%20the%20lawsuit%20was%20based%20on%20incoherent%20claims%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20a%20contrived%20attempt%20by%20Musk%20to%20advance%20his%20own%20AI%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeeing%20the%20remarkable%20technological%20advances%20OpenAI%20has%20achieved%2C%20Musk%20now%20wants%20that%20success%20for%20himself%2C%26quot%3B%20OpenAI's%20attorneys%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20in%20a%20filing%20in%20April%20said%20OpenAI%20was%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Badvance%20arguments%20that%20are%20based%20on%20disputed%20facts%26quot%3B%20that%20are%20beyond%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718146380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fa945hc54_elon-musk_625x300_24_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-withdraws-lawsuit-against-openai-its-ceo-sam-altman-5870639%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20on%20Tuesday%20moved%20to%20dismiss%20his%20lawsuit%20accusing%20ChatGPT%20maker%20OpenAI%20and%20its%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20of%20abandoning%20the%20startup's%20original%20mission%20of%20developing%20artificial%20intelligence%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20humanity%20and%20not%20for%20profit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-withdraws-lawsuit-against-openai-its-ceo-sam-altman-5870639%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-withdraws-lawsuit-against-openai-its-ceo-sam-altman-5870639%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-withdraws-lawsuit-against-openai-its-ceo-sam-altman-5870639%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%