3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Quince%20has%20a%20365-day%20return%20policy%20(yes%2C%20you%20read%20that%20right)%2C%20so%20if%20these%20linen%20sheets%20aren't%20your%20cup%20of%20tea%20after%20trying%20them%20out%2C%20you%20can%20return%20them%20within%20a%20year%20for%20a%20full%20refund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20organic%5C%22%3EBest%20organic%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20Sijo%20sheets%20feel%20like%20what%20you'd%20imagine%20most%20linen%20sheets%20to%20be%3A%20rough%2C%20stiff%2C%20and%20slightly%20itchy.%20While%20this%20set%20may%20not%20be%20the%20softest%20on%20the%20market%2C%20it%20certainly%20makes%20up%20for%20it%20in%20the%20durability%20department%2C%20and%20they%20get%20softer%20with%20each%20wash.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20across%20the%20Insider%20Reviews%20team%20who've%20slept%20on%20the%20sheets%20for%20years%20described%20the%20Sijo%20sheets%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20right%20balance%20of%20comfort%2C%20coolness%2C%20durability%2C%20and%20price.%26quot%3B%20They%20were%20previously%20our%20top%20pick%20for%20the%20best%20linen%20sheets%20%E2%80%94%20only%20to%20be%20edged%20out%20by%20Brooklinen%20for%20their%20out-of-the-packaging%20softness%20%E2%80%94%20and%20rank%20in%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20best%20sheets%20as%20our%20top%20pick%20for%20cooling%20sheets.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20green%20linen%20sheet%20set%20on%20a%20bed%20with%20a%20gray%20duvet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65947fb9ec62ab5daf801f3e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223330%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20addition%20to%20being%20organic%2C%20the%20Sijo%20LuxWeave%20Linen%20set%20is%20a%20great%20option%20for%20those%20who%20are%20looking%20to%20try%20linen%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20with%20a%20design%20that%20gets%20softer%20with%20time%20and%20sleeps%20cool.%3Cp%3EShannon%20Ullman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20initial%20fuzzies%20and%20loose%2C%20white%20strings%20I%20found%20when%20making%20the%20bed%2C%20the%20sheets%20held%20up%20well%20after%20washing%20without%20any%20pilling%20or%20loose%20threads.%20Putting%20on%20the%20fitted%20sheet%20was%20easy%2C%20and%20it%20stayed%20in%20place%20throughout%20the%20night%2C%20but%20I%20did%20find%20myself%20wishing%20for%20top%20and%20bottom%20tags%20as%20a%20reference%20point%2C%20like%20with%20our%20overall%20pick%20from%20Brooklinen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20this%20set%20really%20shines%20is%20in%20its%20vibrant%20color%20options.%20I%20opted%20for%20the%20forest%20green%2C%20but%20there%20are%20eight%20total%20shades%20to%20choose%20from%2C%20and%20the%20set%20comes%20with%20the%20standard%20essentials.%20Linen%20is%20known%20for%20its%20temperature-regulating%20properties%2C%20and%20I%20found%20these%20sheets%20to%20be%20neither%20too%20hot%20nor%20too%20cold.%20So%20if%20you're%20a%20neutral%20sleeper%20looking%20for%20a%20more%20durable%20linen%20option%2C%20the%20LuxWeave%20Linen%20by%20Sijo%20is%20worth%20considering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20cooling%5C%22%3EBest%20cooling%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20prefer%20to%20mix%20and%20match%20their%20bedding%20pieces%2C%20Parachute's%20linen%20sheet%20set%20is%20the%20perfect%20option.%20Sold%20separately%20in%20flat%20sheets%2C%20fitted%20sheets%2C%20and%20pillowcases%2C%20you%20can%20create%20a%20personalized%20set%20with%20only%20the%20pieces%20you%20need.%20They%20even%20offer%20multiple%20pillowcase%20styles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20customization%20perks%2C%20these%20sheets%20were%20practically%20made%20for%20hot%20sleepers.%20The%20ultra-thin%20material%20is%20incredibly%20cooling%20and%20breathable%2C%20with%20a%20lightweight%20feel%20that%20only%20gets%20softer%20with%20each%20wash.%20Plus%2C%20the%20sheets%20themselves%20are%20easy%20to%20put%20on%20the%20bed%2C%20which%20can%20be%20a%20struggle%20with%20thicker%20or%20stiffer%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20brown%20linen%20sheet%20set%20on%20a%20bed%20with%20a%20gray%20duvet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659480271c5c7b8c9a0d69f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223330%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20you%20sleep%20hot%2C%20Parachute%E2%80%99s%20linen%20sheets%20are%20incredibly%20breathable%20and%20lightweight%2C%20making%20them%20ideal%20for%20warmer%20months%2C%20too.%3Cp%3EShannon%20Ullman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMade%20from%20100%25%20European%20flax%20and%20certified%20by%20Oeko-Tex%20Standard%20100%2C%20these%20sheets%20are%20high%20quality%20and%20adhere%20to%20safe%20textile%20production%20practices.%20However%2C%20the%20thin%20material%20may%20not%20be%20as%20durable%20as%20some%20of%20the%20other%20options%20on%20this%20list%2C%20so%20keep%20that%20in%20mind%20if%20you%20tend%20to%20put%20your%20bedding%20through%20the%20wringer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20Parachute%20does%20not%20offer%20a%20storage%20bag%20with%20their%20linen%20sheet%20set.%20But%20they%20do%20offer%20eight%20color%20options%20and%20free%20returns%20within%2060%20days%20%E2%80%94%20plenty%20of%20time%20to%20decide%20if%20these%20sheets%20are%20the%20key%20to%20your%20best%20night's%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fparachute-linen-bed-sheets-review%5C%22%3EParachute%20Linen%20Sheets%20review%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Most%20heavyweight%5C%22%3EMost%20heavyweight%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELinen%20sheets%20tend%20to%20have%20that%20lightweight%20feel%2C%20which%20is%20why%20they're%20a%20popular%20option%20among%20hot%20sleepers.%20But%20if%20you%20like%20your%20bedding%20to%20have%20a%20bit%20more%20heft%20(especially%20during%20those%20cold%20winter%20nights)%2C%20Coyuchi's%20organic%20linen%20set%20may%20be%20right%20up%20your%20alley.%20The%20sheets%20%E2%80%94%20which%20come%20in%20seven%20neutral%20colors%20%E2%80%94%20feel%20heavy%20and%20substantial%20but%20still%20breathable%20enough%20to%20prevent%20waking%20up%20in%20a%20pool%20of%20sweat.%20While%20the%20Sijo%20and%20Coyuchi%20sets%20are%20both%20organic%20and%20durable%2C%20the%20Coyuchi%20definitely%20feels%20more%20heavy-duty.%20If%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20linen%20sheet%20to%20get%20you%20through%20the%20chilly%20winter%20nights%2C%20Coyuchi%20may%20be%20your%20best%20bet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20grey%20linen%20sheet%20set%20on%20a%20bed%20with%20a%20gray%20duvet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65947ff2ec62ab5daf801fb2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223330%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECoyuchi%E2%80%99s%20Organic%20Relaxed%20Linen%20Sheets%20are%20an%20investment%20that%20are%20durable%2C%20well-made%20and%20comfortable%20for%20use%20for%20years%20to%20come.%3Cp%3EShannon%20Ullman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EImmediately%20out%20of%20the%20package%2C%20these%20linen%20sheets%20%3Cem%3Efelt%20%3C%2Fem%3Elike%20linen%20sheets%3A%20stiff%20and%20a%20little%20rough.%20But%20the%20fabric%20definitely%20felt%20durable%2C%20and%20overall%2C%20the%20set%20was%20easy%20to%20throw%20on%20the%20bed.%20I%20did%20notice%20a%20few%20pilling%20spots%20and%20loose%20threads%20on%20the%20fitted%20sheet%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20lack%20of%20top%20and%20bottom%20tags%2C%20which%20isn't%20ideal%20for%20a%20higher-priced%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Coyuchi%20lists%20no%20certifications%2C%20the%20sheets%20are%20made%20from%20100%25%20organic%20French%20flax%2C%20and%20the%20brand%20prides%20itself%20on%20its%20sustainable%20practices.%20Overall%2C%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20luxurious%20and%20organic%20linen%20option%20that%20will%20last%20longer%20than%20most%2C%20Coyuchi's%20Relaxed%20Linen%20Sheets%20are%20worth%20considering.%20Just%20be%20prepared%20to%20spend%20a%20bit%20more%20on%20quality%20and%20sustainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Softest%5C%22%3ESoftest%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWest%20Elm's%20European%20Flax%20Linen%20Sheet%20Set%20is%20a%20game%20changer%20for%20those%20who%20prioritize%20softness%20above%20all%20else.%20You'll%20find%20none%20of%20that%20classic%20linen%20roughness%20here.%20Made%20from%20100%25%20European%20flax%20and%20certified%20by%20Oeko-Tex%20Standard%20100%2C%20these%20sheets%20have%20a%20noticeable%20softness%20right%20out%20of%20the%20package%20that%20only%20gets%20cozier%20with%20each%20wash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20unlike%20cotton-esque%20softness%20that%20can%20feel%20stifling%20and%20hot%2C%20the%20linen%20material%20is%20incredibly%20breathable%20and%20cooling.%20It's%20like%20sleeping%20on%20a%20cloud%20but%20without%20the%20sweat.%20I%20was%20also%20pleasantly%20surprised%20by%20how%20well%20these%20sheets%20held%20up%20in%20the%20wash%20%E2%80%94%20no%20pilling%20or%20shrinking%20issues%20to%20be%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224859%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20gray%20linen%20sheet%20set%20on%20a%20bed%20with%20a%20gray%20duvet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659480571c5c7b8c9a0d6a46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223644%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFor%20those%20who%20prioritize%20all%20things%20soft%2C%20the%20West%20Elm%20European%20Flax%20Linen%20Sheet%20impressed%20us%20for%20its%20immediate%20softness%2C%20breathability%2C%20and%20vast%20color%20selection.%3Cp%3EShannon%20Ullman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20immediate%20softness%20is%20a%20major%20plus%2C%20some%20factors%20make%20me%20question%20how%20durable%20these%20sheets%20will%20be%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20Putting%20on%20the%20fitted%20sheet%20was%20easy%2C%20but%20the%20elastic%20felt%20a%20bit%20flimsy%20and%20loose.%20There%20were%20also%20some%20loose%20threads%20on%20the%20pillowcase%2C%20another%20indicator%20that%20these%20sheets%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20withstand%20heavy%20usage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20willing%20to%20overlook%20those%20concerns%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20ultimate%20softness%2C%20then%20these%20linen%20sheets%20are%20a%20great%20option.%20They%20come%20in%2022%20different%20color%20options%20(note%3A%20some%20hues%20are%20made-to-order%20and%20take%20longer%20to%20receive)%20and%20have%20a%2030-day%20return%20policy%20if%20they%20don't%20live%20up%20to%20your%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20all-season%5C%22%3EBest%20all-season%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20looking%20for%20a%20linen%20sheet%20set%20that%20can%20handle%20the%20thick%20humidity%20of%20July%20and%20the%20blustery%20storms%20of%20December%2C%20look%20no%20further%20than%20The%20Citizenry.%20The%20brand's%20Stonewashed%20Linen%20Sheet%20Set%20weighs%20160%20gsm%2C%20making%20it%20the%20perfect%20middle%20ground%20between%20lightweight%20and%20heavy-duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20right%20in%20the%20middle%3F%20It's%20texture.%20I%20wouldn't%20put%20it%20in%20the%20category%20of%20ultra-rough%20linen%20as%20it%20has%20some%20softness%20to%20it%2C%20but%20it's%20definitely%20not%20like%20curling%20up%20in%20a%20pile%20of%20marshmallows.%20However%2C%20the%20material%20feels%20durable%20and%20high-quality%2C%20giving%20you%20confidence%20that%20these%20sheets%20will%20hold%20up%20well%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20gray%20linen%20sheet%20set%20on%20a%20bed%20with%20a%20gray%20duvet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659480aaab6f2ebb11f84cdc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223330%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Citizenry%20offers%20a%20great%20midweight%20option%20that%E2%80%99s%20suitable%20for%20year-round%20use%3B%20we%20also%20love%20the%20pretty%20hem-stitch%20detail%20on%20the%20top%20sheet.%3Cp%3EShannon%20Ullman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20practicality%2C%20these%20sheets%20are%20a%20dream.%20They're%20easy%20to%20put%20on%20your%20bed%20without%20any%20major%20wrinkling%20or%20shrinking%20post-wash.%20And%20speaking%20of%20washing%2C%20they%20come%20out%20looking%20and%20feeling%20great%20with%20each%20cycle.%20One%20downside%20to%20these%20sheets%20is%20that%20they%20do%20sleep%20slightly%20warm.%20It's%20not%20unbearable%20(especially%20when%20the%20temperatures%20drop)%2C%20but%20it%20could%20be%20an%20issue%20for%20those%20who%20run%20extra-hot%20at%20night.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20good%20news%3F%20You've%20got%2014%20colors%20and%20three%20patterns%20to%20choose%20from%20and%2030%20days%20to%20decide%20if%20these%20sheets%20are%20the%20all-season%20option%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20color%20selection%5C%22%3EBest%20color%20selection%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELinen%20is%20the%20only%20thing%20you%20can%20buy%20from%20MagicLinen%2C%20which%20is%20precisely%20the%20reason%20it's%20been%20able%20to%20edge%20out%20other%20brands%20that%20have%20only%20treated%20the%20material%20as%20one%20more%20piece%20of%20their%20larger%20bedding%20puzzles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20its%20products%20are%20handcrafted%20in%20Vilnius%2C%20Lithuania.%20The%20linen%20is%20stonewashed%20%E2%80%94%20a%20softening%20process%20that's%20completely%20natural%20and%20non-toxic%20%E2%80%94%20and%20OEKO-Tex%20certified%2C%20meaning%20it%20meets%20chemical%20safety%20standards%20and%20is%20free%20from%20harmful%20substances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22best%20linen%20sheets%20magiclinen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61e0981dc5e27c00185b7eaa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMagicLinen%20specializes%20in%20only%20linen%20products%2C%20with%20sheet%20sets%20available%20in%2020%20colors%20and%20a%20deep%20pocket%20option%2C%20too.%3Cp%3EMagicLinen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%C2%A0%3Cp%3EThese%20sheets%20particularly%20stood%20out%20to%20executive%20editor%20Sally%20Kaplan%20because%20they%20come%20in%20deep%20options%20for%20mattresses%20up%20to%2018%20inches%20thick%2C%20a%20sizing%20that's%20usually%20difficult%20to%20find%20for%20linen.%20The%20standard%20size%20fits%20mattresses%20up%20to%2010%20inches%20thick.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Sally%2C%20MagicLinen's%20sheets%20aren't%20the%20softest%20out%20of%20the%20bag%2C%20but%20after%20two%20years%20of%20use%2C%20they've%20aged%20well%3Cstrong%3E%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20getting%20softer%20and%20cozier%20with%20every%20wash.%20MagicLinen%20offers%20a%2030-day%20trial%2C%20but%20return%20shipping%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20not%20sure%20yet%20about%20committing%2C%20you%20can%20get%20fabric%20samples.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-55213-20%26h%3D80a51e013ae9e43d60590476b1c9bb66a08edfdfabdf318448e5aba6e15f67df%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f42e6d%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-linen-sheets%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fmagiclinen.com%252Fproducts%252Fhome-textiles-fabric-sample-set%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eset%20of%20all%20the%20colors%3C%2Fa%3E%20only%20costs%20%245%2C%20plus%20you'll%20get%20a%20%245%20discount%20off%20your%20next%20purchase.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fmagiclinen-bedding-deep-sheets-review%5C%22%3EMagicLinen%20linen%20sheet%20set%20review%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20linen%20sheets%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20linen%20sheets%20are%20created%20equal.%20So%20we%20consulted%20with%20Frej%20Lewenhaupt%2C%20textile%20expert%2C%20co-founder%2C%20and%20CEO%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsteamery.us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Steamery%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20on%20the%20telltale%20signs%20that%20a%20set%20of%20linen%20sheets%20is%20worth%20investing%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFiber%20Content%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELewenhaupt%20says%20a%20good%20rule%20of%20thumb%20is%20that%20the%20fewer%20synthetic%20fibers%20on%20a%20label%2C%20the%20better.%20If%20a%20brand%20lists%20out%20more%20than%20four%20fibers%20in%20its%20blend%20or%20doesn't%20advertise%20specific%20percentages%2C%20that's%20a%20red%20flag.%20Aim%20for%20linen%20sheets%20made%20with%20100%25%20flax.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlax%20Origin%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELinen%20is%20constructed%20out%20of%20the%20flax%20plant%20%E2%80%94%20and%20where%20that%20plant%20is%20grown%20can%20make%20a%20huge%20difference%20in%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20final%20product.%20Flax%20linen%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC4403609%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etypically%3C%2Fa%3E%20soft%2C%20durable%2C%20temperature-regulating%2C%20and%20absorbent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%3A%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELinen's%20weight%20is%20measured%20in%20grams%20per%20square%20meter%20(GSM.)%20A%20high%20GSM%20will%20typically%20result%20in%20a%20denser%20fabric%2C%20while%20a%20lower%20GSM%20might%20feel%20more%20lightweight.%20Linen%20tends%20to%20be%20either%20lightweight%20or%20medium-weight.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20lightweight%20linen%20may%20be%20about%20130%20GSM%2C%20while%20a%20medium-weight%20linen%20could%20be%20150%20to%20350%20GSM.%20The%20higher%20the%20GSM%2C%20the%20warmer%20the%20linen%20sheet%20might%20feel%20while%20sleeping.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECertifications%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELook%20for%20certifications%20like%20Oeko-Tex%20Standard%20100%2C%20which%20confirms%20that%20a%20product%20is%20free%20of%20harmful%20chemicals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20tested%20linen%20sheets%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20determine%20which%20linen%20sheets%20are%20really%20worth%20your%20while%2C%20I%20tested%2010%20of%20the%20most%20highly-rated%20sets%20and%20slept%20on%20them%20for%20multiple%20nights%20to%20measure%20their%20feel%2C%20weight%2C%20durability%2C%20and%20overall%20comfort.%20Each%20set%20was%20tested%20for%20three%20nights%20in%20a%20row%20and%20washed%20and%20dried%20once.%20I%20also%20consulted%20with%20experts%2C%20like%20Frej%20Lewenhaupt%2C%20a%20textile%20expert%2C%20cofounder%2C%20and%20CEO%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsteamery.us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Steamery%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uri.edu%2Fnews%2F2018%2F04%2Ftextiles-group-renames-scholarship-after-uri-professor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMartin%20Bide%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20professor%20in%20the%20department%20of%20textiles%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Rhode%20Island%2C%20for%20insights%20on%20which%20factors%20I%20should%20pay%20special%20attention%20to.%20These%20are%20the%20factors%20I%20took%20into%20consideration%20when%20testing%20each%20set%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImmediate%20softness%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELinen%20gets%20a%20bad%20rap%20for%20being%20rough%20and%20scratchy%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20always%20the%20case.%20I%20noted%20how%20soft%20each%20set%20felt%20upon%20first%20touch%20and%20snooze.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20considered%20the%20weight%20(GSM)%20of%20each%20set.%20The%20higher%20the%20GSM%2C%20the%20heavier%20and%20thicker%20the%20material.%20I%20kept%20the%20weight%20of%20each%20set%20in%20mind%20and%20whether%20it%20resulted%20in%20a%20hotter%20or%20cooler%20sleep%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPost-wash%20feel%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESome%20sheets%20come%20out%20of%20the%20dryer%20looking%20and%20feeling%20like%20they've%20been%20through%20a%20war.%20Others%2C%20not%20so%20much.%20After%20washing%20and%20drying%20each%20set%2C%20I%20looked%20for%20any%20signs%20of%20pilling%2C%20shedding%2C%20shrinking%2C%20or%20wrinkling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3A%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe've%20all%20wrestled%20with%20a%20fitted%20sheet%20at%20some%20point.%20I%20noted%20how%20easy%20(or%20difficult)%20it%20was%20to%20get%20each%20set%20onto%20the%20bed%20without%20any%20significant%20wrinkles%2C%20creases%2C%20or%20bunching.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Linen's%20durability%20is%20a%20big%20selling%20point%20for%20many%2C%20as%20the%20textile%20can%20last%20years%20if%20properly%20cared%20for.%20I%20looked%20for%20signs%20of%20wear%20and%20tear%20and%20how%20durable%20the%20material%20felt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3ELinen%20sheets%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20linen%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ELinen%20is%20an%20all-natural%20fiber%20from%20the%20flax%20plant.%20Its%20long%20and%20strong%20fibers%20make%20it%20a%20more%20durable%20fabric%20that%20is%20also%20highly%20absorbent%2C%20naturally%20moisture-wicking%2C%20and%20dries%20quickly%20compared%20to%20other%20options%20like%20cotton.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20linen%20so%20expensive%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ELinen%20is%20expensive%20because%20it%20can%20only%20be%20grown%20in%20certain%20locations%2C%20and%20the%20production%20process%20is%20labor-intensive.%20Flax%20plants%20prefer%20cooler%20climates%20and%20are%20typically%20grown%20in%C2%A0%20European%20locations%20like%20Belgium.%20The%20growing%20and%20processing%20of%20flax%20plants%20into%20linen%20is%20time-consuming%20and%20labor-intensive%2C%20which%20drives%20up%20the%20price.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20care%20for%20linen%20sheets%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ELinen%20sheets%20aren't%20exactly%20high%20maintenance%2C%20but%20there%20are%20a%20few%20tips%20for%20keeping%20your%20linen%20sheets%20well-cared%20for.%20When%20washing%20linen%20sheets%2C%20avoid%20hot%20water%20that%20could%20break%20down%20the%20fibers.%20Instead%2C%20opt%20for%20warm%20water%20and%20a%20delicate%20wash%20setting.%20Try%20to%20avoid%20harsh%20chemicals%20in%20laundry%20detergents%20that%20could%20break%20down%20linen%20fibers%20and%20cause%20discoloration.%20Consider%20air-drying%20linen%20sheets%20to%20preserve%20durability%2C%20but%20using%20a%20dryer%20on%20a%20low%20heat%2C%20tumble%20setting%20should%20work%20just%20fine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20buy%20linen%20sheets%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20enjoying%20the%20aesthetic%2C%20Bide%20recommends%20linen%20sheets%20for%20hot%20sleepers%20or%20anyone%20who%20enjoys%20a%20cooler%20sleep%20since%20linen%20is%20absorbent%20and%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bcool%26quot%3B%20feel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ELinen%20sheets%20vs.%20cotton%20%E2%80%94%20What's%20the%20difference%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ELewenhaupt%20says%20linen%20is%20typically%20more%20durable%20than%20cotton%20as%20the%20fibers%20have%20a%20longer%20and%20more%20open%20structure.%20This%20structure%20makes%20linen%20more%20absorbent%2C%20which%20is%20what%20gives%20them%20that%20cooling%20sensation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20linen%20sheets%20good%20for%20hot%20sleepers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Bide%2C%20yes.%20He%20says%20that%20linen%20is%20known%20to%20be%20absorbent%2C%20hence%20its%20use%20for%20dish%20towels%20and%20old-fashioned%20handkerchiefs.%20You're%20unlikely%20to%20get%20that%20%26quot%3Bclammy%26quot%3B%20feeling%20from%20a%20linen%20sheet%2C%20making%20it%20a%20great%20option%20for%20hot%20sleepers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20linen%20sheets%20best%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20%26quot%3Bbest%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20sheets%2C%20as%20what%20you%20sleep%20on%20is%20largely%20a%20matter%20of%20personal%20preference.%20However%2C%20linen%20sheets%20tend%20to%20be%20durable%20and%20long-lasting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20quality%20linen%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ELinen%20made%20from%20Flax%20grown%20in%20France%20or%20Belgium%20is%20the%20highest%20quality%2C%20according%20to%20Lewenhaupt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20hotels%20use%20linen%20sheets%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20hotels%20use%20linen%20sheets%2C%20but%20most%20use%20high-quality%20cotton%20sheets%20in%20their%20bedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20you%20sleep%20better%20with%20linen%20sheets%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20scientific%20evidence%20that%20linen%20sheets%20help%20you%20sleep%20better%2C%20as%20the%20material%20you%20sleep%20best%20on%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20preference.%20But%20if%20you%20tend%20to%20sleep%20hot%2C%20the%20breathability%20of%20linen%20may%20be%20beneficial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20overall%3A%20Brooklinen%20Washed%20Linen%20Core%20Sheet%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Blue%20linen%20sheet%20set%20on%20a%20bed%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65947f47ec62ab5daf801eed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223330%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrooklinen%E2%80%99s%20Washed%20Linen%20sheets%20were%20like%20sleeping%20on%20a%20cloud%3A%20soft%2C%20breathable%20and%20lightweight%3Cp%3EShannon%20Ullman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20all%20of%20the%20linen%20sets%20I%20tried%20claimed%20to%20be%20soft%2C%20some%20still%20had%20an%20underlying%20roughness%20or%20stiffness%20to%20them.%20Not%20the%20case%20here%20%E2%80%94%20this%20Brooklinen%20set%20felt%20like%20sleeping%20on%20a%20cloud%20straight%20out%20of%20the%20bag.%20There%20was%20no%20itchiness%3B%20the%20sheets%20only%20got%20softer%20with%20each%20wash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20weight%20is%20also%20perfect%20for%20hot%20sleepers.%20Typically%2C%20linen%20sheets%20indicate%20a%20heavier%20material%20that%20leaves%20some%20people%20feeling%20trapped%20and%20overheated.%20But%20this%20linen%20set%20is%20thin%20and%20light%20enough%20to%20maintain%20a%20cool%20temperature%20throughout%20the%20night.%20Some%20lightweight%20sheets%20can%20feel%20flimsy%2C%20but%20these%20had%20a%20high-quality%20feel%20that%20held%20up%20nicely%20without%20any%20rips%20or%20tears.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20packaging%20was%20also%20a%20nice%20touch%2C%20coming%20in%20a%20cloth%20bag%20for%20storage.%20In%20terms%20of%20durability%2C%20I%20did%20notice%20some%20slight%20pilling%20after%20washing%2C%20but%20nothing%20that%20affected%20the%20overall%20feel%20or%20comfort%20of%20the%20sheets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnyone%20who%20cares%20about%20the%20aesthetic%20of%20their%20bedding%20will%20love%20that%20there%20are%20five%20colors%20to%20choose%20from%2C%20as%20well%20as%20some%20limited%20edition%20palettes.%20The%20set%20comes%20with%20the%20standard%20essentials%3A%20a%20flat%20sheet%2C%20a%20fitted%20sheet%2C%20and%20two%20pillowcases%2C%20but%20Brooklinen%20also%20sells%20individual%20pieces%20and%20sets%20without%20a%20flat%20sheet%20if%20that's%20your%20preference.%20Most%20Brooklinen%20items%20can%20be%20returned%20within%20a%20year%2C%20but%20you%20are%20subjected%20to%20a%20%249.95%20return%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbrooklinen-linen-bed-sheets-review%5C%22%3EBrooklinen%20Washed%20Linen%20Sheets%20review%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20budget%3A%20Quince%20Linen%20Sheet%20Set%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20orange%20linen%20sheet%20set%20on%20a%20bed%20with%20a%20gray%20duvet.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65947f82ec62ab5daf801f0b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223330%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EQuince%E2%80%99s%20linen%20sheet%20set%20is%20available%20in%20over%2020%20colors%20and%20cost%20under%20%24200%2C%20making%20it%20one%20of%20the%20most%20affordable%20sets.%3Cp%3EShannon%20Ullman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20color%20options%2C%20Quince's%20linen%20sheets%20reign%20supreme%2C%20with%20over%2020%20different%20shades%20to%20snuggle%20under.%20From%20a%20deep%20Bordeaux%20to%20the%20ultra-airy%20sage%20or%20a%20timeless%20terracotta%20and%20white%20stripe%2C%20there's%20a%20color%20for%20every%20taste%20and%20bedroom%20aesthetic.%20But%20these%20sheets%20aren't%20just%20about%20looks%20%E2%80%94%20they%20also%20deliver%20on%20comfort%20and%20durability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMade%20from%20100%25%20European%20flax%2C%20these%20sheets%20have%20a%20soft%20feel%20that%20falls%20directly%20in%20between%20Brooklinen's%20Washed%20Linen%20Core%20Sheets%20and%20Sijo's%20LuxeWeave%20Linen%20Sheets.%20The%20material%20was%20quite%20luxurious%20and%20inviting%2C%20albeit%20a%20bit%20warm.%20So%2C%20if%20you%20sleep%20on%20the%20hotter%20side%2C%20you%20might%20want%20to%20give%20these%20thicker%20sheets%20a%20pass.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuince%20also%20passed%20the%20test%20for%20two%20major%20sheet%20sticking%20points%3A%20pilling%20and%20bed-making.%20The%20fitted%20sheet%20comes%20with%20those%20handy%20top%20and%20bottom%20tags%2C%20and%20both%20layers%20went%20through%20the%20wash%20without%20pilling.%20For%20those%20who%20like%20a%20monochromatic%20look%2C%20Quince%20also%20has%20duvet%20covers%20in%20the%20same%20color%20options%20as%20the%20sheets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Quince%20has%20a%20365-day%20return%20policy%20(yes%2C%20you%20read%20that%20right)%2C%20so%20if%20these%20linen%20sheets%20aren't%20your%20cup%20of%20tea%20after%20trying%20them%20out%2C%20you%20can%20return%20them%20within%20a%20year%20for%20a%20full%20refund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20organic%3A%20Sijo%20LuxWeave%20Linen%20Sheet%20Set%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20green%20linen%20sheet%20set%20on%20a%20bed%20with%20a%20gray%20duvet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65947fb9ec62ab5daf801f3e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223330%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20addition%20to%20being%20organic%2C%20the%20Sijo%20LuxWeave%20Linen%20set%20is%20a%20great%20option%20for%20those%20who%20are%20looking%20to%20try%20linen%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20with%20a%20design%20that%20gets%20softer%20with%20time%20and%20sleeps%20cool.%3Cp%3EShannon%20Ullman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20Sijo%20sheets%20feel%20like%20what%20you'd%20imagine%20most%20linen%20sheets%20to%20be%3A%20rough%2C%20stiff%2C%20and%20slightly%20itchy.%20While%20this%20set%20may%20not%20be%20the%20softest%20on%20the%20market%2C%20it%20certainly%20makes%20up%20for%20it%20in%20the%20durability%20department%2C%20and%20they%20get%20softer%20with%20each%20wash.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20across%20the%20Insider%20Reviews%20team%20who've%20slept%20on%20the%20sheets%20for%20years%20described%20the%20Sijo%20sheets%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20right%20balance%20of%20comfort%2C%20coolness%2C%20durability%2C%20and%20price.%26quot%3B%20They%20were%20previously%20our%20top%20pick%20for%20the%20best%20linen%20sheets%20%E2%80%94%20only%20to%20be%20edged%20out%20by%20Brooklinen%20for%20their%20out-of-the-packaging%20softness%20%E2%80%94%20and%20rank%20in%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20best%20sheets%20as%20our%20top%20pick%20for%20cooling%20sheets.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20initial%20fuzzies%20and%20loose%2C%20white%20strings%20I%20found%20when%20making%20the%20bed%2C%20the%20sheets%20held%20up%20well%20after%20washing%20without%20any%20pilling%20or%20loose%20threads.%20Putting%20on%20the%20fitted%20sheet%20was%20easy%2C%20and%20it%20stayed%20in%20place%20throughout%20the%20night%2C%20but%20I%20did%20find%20myself%20wishing%20for%20top%20and%20bottom%20tags%20as%20a%20reference%20point%2C%20like%20with%20our%20overall%20pick%20from%20Brooklinen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhere%20this%20set%20really%20shines%20is%20in%20its%20vibrant%20color%20options.%20I%20opted%20for%20the%20forest%20green%2C%20but%20there%20are%20eight%20total%20shades%20to%20choose%20from%2C%20and%20the%20set%20comes%20with%20the%20standard%20essentials.%20Linen%20is%20known%20for%20its%20temperature-regulating%20properties%2C%20and%20I%20found%20these%20sheets%20to%20be%20neither%20too%20hot%20nor%20too%20cold.%20So%20if%20you're%20a%20neutral%20sleeper%20looking%20for%20a%20more%20durable%20linen%20option%2C%20the%20LuxWeave%20Linen%20by%20Sijo%20is%20worth%20considering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20cooling%3A%20Parachute%20Linen%20Sheet%20Set%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20brown%20linen%20sheet%20set%20on%20a%20bed%20with%20a%20gray%20duvet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659480271c5c7b8c9a0d69f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223330%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20you%20sleep%20hot%2C%20Parachute%E2%80%99s%20linen%20sheets%20are%20incredibly%20breathable%20and%20lightweight%2C%20making%20them%20ideal%20for%20warmer%20months%2C%20too.%3Cp%3EShannon%20Ullman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20prefer%20to%20mix%20and%20match%20their%20bedding%20pieces%2C%20Parachute's%20linen%20sheet%20set%20is%20the%20perfect%20option.%20Sold%20separately%20in%20flat%20sheets%2C%20fitted%20sheets%2C%20and%20pillowcases%2C%20you%20can%20create%20a%20personalized%20set%20with%20only%20the%20pieces%20you%20need.%20They%20even%20offer%20multiple%20pillowcase%20styles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20the%20customization%20perks%2C%20these%20sheets%20were%20practically%20made%20for%20hot%20sleepers.%20The%20ultra-thin%20material%20is%20incredibly%20cooling%20and%20breathable%2C%20with%20a%20lightweight%20feel%20that%20only%20gets%20softer%20with%20each%20wash.%20Plus%2C%20the%20sheets%20themselves%20are%20easy%20to%20put%20on%20the%20bed%2C%20which%20can%20be%20a%20struggle%20with%20thicker%20or%20stiffer%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMade%20from%20100%25%20European%20flax%20and%20certified%20by%20Oeko-Tex%20Standard%20100%2C%20these%20sheets%20are%20high%20quality%20and%20adhere%20to%20safe%20textile%20production%20practices.%20However%2C%20the%20thin%20material%20may%20not%20be%20as%20durable%20as%20some%20of%20the%20other%20options%20on%20this%20list%2C%20so%20keep%20that%20in%20mind%20if%20you%20tend%20to%20put%20your%20bedding%20through%20the%20wringer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20Parachute%20does%20not%20offer%20a%20storage%20bag%20with%20their%20linen%20sheet%20set.%20But%20they%20do%20offer%20eight%20color%20options%20and%20free%20returns%20within%2060%20days%20%E2%80%94%20plenty%20of%20time%20to%20decide%20if%20these%20sheets%20are%20the%20key%20to%20your%20best%20night's%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fparachute-linen-bed-sheets-review%5C%22%3EParachute%20Linen%20Sheets%20review%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMost%20heavyweight%3A%20Coyuchi%20Organic%20Relaxed%20Linen%20Sheets%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20grey%20linen%20sheet%20set%20on%20a%20bed%20with%20a%20gray%20duvet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65947ff2ec62ab5daf801fb2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223330%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECoyuchi%E2%80%99s%20Organic%20Relaxed%20Linen%20Sheets%20are%20an%20investment%20that%20are%20durable%2C%20well-made%20and%20comfortable%20for%20use%20for%20years%20to%20come.%3Cp%3EShannon%20Ullman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELinen%20sheets%20tend%20to%20have%20that%20lightweight%20feel%2C%20which%20is%20why%20they're%20a%20popular%20option%20among%20hot%20sleepers.%20But%20if%20you%20like%20your%20bedding%20to%20have%20a%20bit%20more%20heft%20(especially%20during%20those%20cold%20winter%20nights)%2C%20Coyuchi's%20organic%20linen%20set%20may%20be%20right%20up%20your%20alley.%20The%20sheets%20%E2%80%94%20which%20come%20in%20seven%20neutral%20colors%20%E2%80%94%20feel%20heavy%20and%20substantial%20but%20still%20breathable%20enough%20to%20prevent%20waking%20up%20in%20a%20pool%20of%20sweat.%20While%20the%20Sijo%20and%20Coyuchi%20sets%20are%20both%20organic%20and%20durable%2C%20the%20Coyuchi%20definitely%20feels%20more%20heavy-duty.%20If%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20linen%20sheet%20to%20get%20you%20through%20the%20chilly%20winter%20nights%2C%20Coyuchi%20may%20be%20your%20best%20bet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImmediately%20out%20of%20the%20package%2C%20these%20linen%20sheets%20%3Cem%3Efelt%20%3C%2Fem%3Elike%20linen%20sheets%3A%20stiff%20and%20a%20little%20rough.%20But%20the%20fabric%20definitely%20felt%20durable%2C%20and%20overall%2C%20the%20set%20was%20easy%20to%20throw%20on%20the%20bed.%20I%20did%20notice%20a%20few%20pilling%20spots%20and%20loose%20threads%20on%20the%20fitted%20sheet%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20lack%20of%20top%20and%20bottom%20tags%2C%20which%20isn't%20ideal%20for%20a%20higher-priced%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Coyuchi%20lists%20no%20certifications%2C%20the%20sheets%20are%20made%20from%20100%25%20organic%20French%20flax%2C%20and%20the%20brand%20prides%20itself%20on%20its%20sustainable%20practices.%20Overall%2C%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20luxurious%20and%20organic%20linen%20option%20that%20will%20last%20longer%20than%20most%2C%20Coyuchi's%20Relaxed%20Linen%20Sheets%20are%20worth%20considering.%20Just%20be%20prepared%20to%20spend%20a%20bit%20more%20on%20quality%20and%20sustainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESoftest%3A%20West%20Elm%20European%20Flax%20Linen%20Sheet%20Set%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224859%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20gray%20linen%20sheet%20set%20on%20a%20bed%20with%20a%20gray%20duvet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659480571c5c7b8c9a0d6a46%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223644%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFor%20those%20who%20prioritize%20all%20things%20soft%2C%20the%20West%20Elm%20European%20Flax%20Linen%20Sheet%20impressed%20us%20for%20its%20immediate%20softness%2C%20breathability%2C%20and%20vast%20color%20selection.%3Cp%3EShannon%20Ullman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWest%20Elm's%20European%20Flax%20Linen%20Sheet%20Set%20is%20a%20game%20changer%20for%20those%20who%20prioritize%20softness%20above%20all%20else.%20You'll%20find%20none%20of%20that%20classic%20linen%20roughness%20here.%20Made%20from%20100%25%20European%20flax%20and%20certified%20by%20Oeko-Tex%20Standard%20100%2C%20these%20sheets%20have%20a%20noticeable%20softness%20right%20out%20of%20the%20package%20that%20only%20gets%20cozier%20with%20each%20wash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20unlike%20cotton-esque%20softness%20that%20can%20feel%20stifling%20and%20hot%2C%20the%20linen%20material%20is%20incredibly%20breathable%20and%20cooling.%20It's%20like%20sleeping%20on%20a%20cloud%20but%20without%20the%20sweat.%20I%20was%20also%20pleasantly%20surprised%20by%20how%20well%20these%20sheets%20held%20up%20in%20the%20wash%20%E2%80%94%20no%20pilling%20or%20shrinking%20issues%20to%20be%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20immediate%20softness%20is%20a%20major%20plus%2C%20some%20factors%20make%20me%20question%20how%20durable%20these%20sheets%20will%20be%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20Putting%20on%20the%20fitted%20sheet%20was%20easy%2C%20but%20the%20elastic%20felt%20a%20bit%20flimsy%20and%20loose.%20There%20were%20also%20some%20loose%20threads%20on%20the%20pillowcase%2C%20another%20indicator%20that%20these%20sheets%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20withstand%20heavy%20usage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20willing%20to%20overlook%20those%20concerns%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20ultimate%20softness%2C%20then%20these%20linen%20sheets%20are%20a%20great%20option.%20They%20come%20in%2022%20different%20color%20options%20(note%3A%20some%20hues%20are%20made-to-order%20and%20take%20longer%20to%20receive)%20and%20have%20a%2030-day%20return%20policy%20if%20they%20don't%20live%20up%20to%20your%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20all-season%3A%20The%20Citizenry%20Stonewashed%20Linen%20Sheet%20Set%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20gray%20linen%20sheet%20set%20on%20a%20bed%20with%20a%20gray%20duvet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659480aaab6f2ebb11f84cdc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223330%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Citizenry%20offers%20a%20great%20midweight%20option%20that%E2%80%99s%20suitable%20for%20year-round%20use%3B%20we%20also%20love%20the%20pretty%20hem-stitch%20detail%20on%20the%20top%20sheet.%3Cp%3EShannon%20Ullman%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20looking%20for%20a%20linen%20sheet%20set%20that%20can%20handle%20the%20thick%20humidity%20of%20July%20and%20the%20blustery%20storms%20of%20December%2C%20look%20no%20further%20than%20The%20Citizenry.%20The%20brand's%20Stonewashed%20Linen%20Sheet%20Set%20weighs%20160%20gsm%2C%20making%20it%20the%20perfect%20middle%20ground%20between%20lightweight%20and%20heavy-duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20right%20in%20the%20middle%3F%20It's%20texture.%20I%20wouldn't%20put%20it%20in%20the%20category%20of%20ultra-rough%20linen%20as%20it%20has%20some%20softness%20to%20it%2C%20but%20it's%20definitely%20not%20like%20curling%20up%20in%20a%20pile%20of%20marshmallows.%20However%2C%20the%20material%20feels%20durable%20and%20high-quality%2C%20giving%20you%20confidence%20that%20these%20sheets%20will%20hold%20up%20well%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20practicality%2C%20these%20sheets%20are%20a%20dream.%20They're%20easy%20to%20put%20on%20your%20bed%20without%20any%20major%20wrinkling%20or%20shrinking%20post-wash.%20And%20speaking%20of%20washing%2C%20they%20come%20out%20looking%20and%20feeling%20great%20with%20each%20cycle.%20One%20downside%20to%20these%20sheets%20is%20that%20they%20do%20sleep%20slightly%20warm.%20It's%20not%20unbearable%20(especially%20when%20the%20temperatures%20drop)%2C%20but%20it%20could%20be%20an%20issue%20for%20those%20who%20run%20extra-hot%20at%20night.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20good%20news%3F%20You've%20got%2014%20colors%20and%20three%20patterns%20to%20choose%20from%20and%2030%20days%20to%20decide%20if%20these%20sheets%20are%20the%20all-season%20option%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20color%20selection%3A%20MagicLinen%20Sheet%20Set%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20bed%20on%20a%20wooden%20platform%20inside%20a%20bedroom%20made%20with%20mint%20green%20linen%20sheets.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ef229703f73700ad919c654%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMagicLinen%20specializes%20in%20only%20linen%20products%2C%20with%20sheet%20sets%20available%20in%2020%20colors%20and%20a%20deep%20pocket%20option%2C%20too.%3Cp%3EMagicLinen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELinen%20is%20the%20only%20thing%20you%20can%20buy%20from%20MagicLinen%2C%20which%20is%20precisely%20the%20reason%20it's%20been%20able%20to%20edge%20out%20other%20brands%20that%20have%20only%20treated%20the%20material%20as%20one%20more%20piece%20of%20their%20larger%20bedding%20puzzles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20its%20products%20are%20handcrafted%20in%20Vilnius%2C%20Lithuania.%20The%20linen%20is%20stonewashed%20%E2%80%94%20a%20softening%20process%20that's%20completely%20natural%20and%20non-toxic%20%E2%80%94%20and%20OEKO-Tex%20certified%2C%20meaning%20it%20meets%20chemical%20safety%20standards%20and%20is%20free%20from%20harmful%20substances.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20sheets%20particularly%20stood%20out%20to%20executive%20editor%20Sally%20Kaplan%20because%20they%20come%20in%20deep%20options%20for%20mattresses%20up%20to%2018%20inches%20thick%2C%20a%20sizing%20that's%20usually%20difficult%20to%20find%20for%20linen.%20The%20standard%20size%20fits%20mattresses%20up%20to%2010%20inches%20thick.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Sally%2C%20MagicLinen's%20sheets%20aren't%20the%20softest%20out%20of%20the%20bag%2C%20but%20after%20two%20years%20of%20use%2C%20they've%20aged%20well%3Cstrong%3E%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20getting%20softer%20and%20cozier%20with%20every%20wash.%20MagicLinen%20offers%20a%2030-day%20trial%2C%20but%20return%20shipping%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20not%20sure%20yet%20about%20committing%2C%20you%20can%20get%20fabric%20samples.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-55213-20%26h%3D80a51e013ae9e43d60590476b1c9bb66a08edfdfabdf318448e5aba6e15f67df%26postID%3D61b8efc8f2a36b1ac9f42e6d%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-linen-sheets%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fmagiclinen.com%252Fproducts%252Fhome-textiles-fabric-sample-set%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eset%20of%20all%20the%20colors%3C%2Fa%3E%20only%20costs%20%245%2C%20plus%20you'll%20get%20a%20%245%20discount%20off%20your%20next%20purchase.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fmagiclinen-bedding-deep-sheets-review%5C%22%3EMagicLinen%20linen%20sheet%20set%20review%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20set%20of%20linen%20sheets%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20linen%20sheets%20are%20created%20equal.%20So%20we%20consulted%20with%20Frej%20Lewenhaupt%2C%20textile%20expert%2C%20co-founder%2C%20and%20CEO%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsteamery.us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Steamery%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20on%20the%20telltale%20signs%20that%20a%20set%20of%20linen%20sheets%20is%20worth%20investing%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFiber%20Content%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELewenhaupt%20says%20a%20good%20rule%20of%20thumb%20is%20that%20the%20fewer%20synthetic%20fibers%20on%20a%20label%2C%20the%20better.%20If%20a%20brand%20lists%20out%20more%20than%20four%20fibers%20in%20its%20blend%20or%20doesn't%20advertise%20specific%20percentages%2C%20that's%20a%20red%20flag.%20Aim%20for%20linen%20sheets%20made%20with%20100%25%20flax.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlax%20Origin%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELinen%20is%20constructed%20out%20of%20the%20flax%20plant%20%E2%80%94%20and%20where%20that%20plant%20is%20grown%20can%20make%20a%20huge%20difference%20in%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20final%20product.%20Flax%20linen%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC4403609%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etypically%3C%2Fa%3E%20soft%2C%20durable%2C%20temperature-regulating%2C%20and%20absorbent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%3A%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELinen's%20weight%20is%20measured%20in%20grams%20per%20square%20meter%20(GSM.)%20A%20high%20GSM%20will%20typically%20result%20in%20a%20denser%20fabric%2C%20while%20a%20lower%20GSM%20might%20feel%20more%20lightweight.%20Linen%20tends%20to%20be%20either%20lightweight%20or%20medium-weight.%20For%20example%2C%20a%20lightweight%20linen%20may%20be%20about%20130%20GSM%2C%20while%20a%20medium-weight%20linen%20could%20be%20150%20to%20350%20GSM.%20The%20higher%20the%20GSM%2C%20the%20warmer%20the%20linen%20sheet%20might%20feel%20while%20sleeping.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECertifications%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELook%20for%20certifications%20like%20Oeko-Tex%20Standard%20100%2C%20which%20confirms%20that%20a%20product%20is%20free%20of%20harmful%20chemicals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20tested%3Cp%3ETo%20determine%20which%20linen%20sheets%20are%20really%20worth%20your%20while%2C%20I%20tested%2010%20of%20the%20most%20highly-rated%20sets%20and%20slept%20on%20them%20for%20multiple%20nights%20to%20measure%20their%20feel%2C%20weight%2C%20durability%2C%20and%20overall%20comfort.%20Each%20set%20was%20tested%20for%20three%20nights%20in%20a%20row%20and%20washed%20and%20dried%20once.%20I%20also%20consulted%20with%20experts%2C%20like%20Frej%20Lewenhaupt%2C%20a%20textile%20expert%2C%20cofounder%2C%20and%20CEO%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsteamery.us%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Steamery%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uri.edu%2Fnews%2F2018%2F04%2Ftextiles-group-renames-scholarship-after-uri-professor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMartin%20Bide%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20professor%20in%20the%20department%20of%20textiles%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Rhode%20Island%2C%20for%20insights%20on%20which%20factors%20I%20should%20pay%20special%20attention%20to.%20These%20are%20the%20factors%20I%20took%20into%20consideration%20when%20testing%20each%20set%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImmediate%20softness%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELinen%20gets%20a%20bad%20rap%20for%20being%20rough%20and%20scratchy%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20always%20the%20case.%20I%20noted%20how%20soft%20each%20set%20felt%20upon%20first%20touch%20and%20snooze.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20considered%20the%20weight%20(GSM)%20of%20each%20set.%20The%20higher%20the%20GSM%2C%20the%20heavier%20and%20thicker%20the%20material.%20I%20kept%20the%20weight%20of%20each%20set%20in%20mind%20and%20whether%20it%20resulted%20in%20a%20hotter%20or%20cooler%20sleep%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPost-wash%20feel%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESome%20sheets%20come%20out%20of%20the%20dryer%20looking%20and%20feeling%20like%20they've%20been%20through%20a%20war.%20Others%2C%20not%20so%20much.%20After%20washing%20and%20drying%20each%20set%2C%20I%20looked%20for%20any%20signs%20of%20pilling%2C%20shedding%2C%20shrinking%2C%20or%20wrinkling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3A%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe've%20all%20wrestled%20with%20a%20fitted%20sheet%20at%20some%20point.%20I%20noted%20how%20easy%20(or%20difficult)%20it%20was%20to%20get%20each%20set%20onto%20the%20bed%20without%20any%20significant%20wrinkles%2C%20creases%2C%20or%20bunching.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Linen's%20durability%20is%20a%20big%20selling%20point%20for%20many%2C%20as%20the%20textile%20can%20last%20years%20if%20properly%20cared%20for.%20I%20looked%20for%20signs%20of%20wear%20and%20tear%20and%20how%20durable%20the%20material%20felt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFAQ%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20linen%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ELinen%20is%20an%20all-natural%20fiber%20from%20the%20flax%20plant.%20Its%20long%20and%20strong%20fibers%20make%20it%20a%20more%20durable%20fabric%20that%20is%20also%20highly%20absorbent%2C%20naturally%20moisture-wicking%2C%20and%20dries%20quickly%20compared%20to%20other%20options%20like%20cotton.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20linen%20so%20expensive%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ELinen%20is%20expensive%20because%20it%20can%20only%20be%20grown%20in%20certain%20locations%2C%20and%20the%20production%20process%20is%20labor-intensive.%20Flax%20plants%20prefer%20cooler%20climates%20and%20are%20typically%20grown%20in%C2%A0%20European%20locations%20like%20Belgium.%20The%20growing%20and%20processing%20of%20flax%20plants%20into%20linen%20is%20time-consuming%20and%20labor-intensive%2C%20which%20drives%20up%20the%20price.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20care%20for%20linen%20sheets%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ELinen%20sheets%20aren't%20exactly%20high%20maintenance%2C%20but%20there%20are%20a%20few%20tips%20for%20keeping%20your%20linen%20sheets%20well-cared%20for.%20When%20washing%20linen%20sheets%2C%20avoid%20hot%20water%20that%20could%20break%20down%20the%20fibers.%20Instead%2C%20opt%20for%20warm%20water%20and%20a%20delicate%20wash%20setting.%20Try%20to%20avoid%20harsh%20chemicals%20in%20laundry%20detergents%20that%20could%20break%20down%20linen%20fibers%20and%20cause%20discoloration.%20Consider%20air-drying%20linen%20sheets%20to%20preserve%20durability%2C%20but%20using%20a%20dryer%20on%20a%20low%20heat%2C%20tumble%20setting%20should%20work%20just%20fine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20buy%20linen%20sheets%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20enjoying%20the%20aesthetic%2C%20Bide%20recommends%20linen%20sheets%20for%20hot%20sleepers%20or%20anyone%20who%20enjoys%20a%20cooler%20sleep%20since%20linen%20is%20absorbent%20and%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bcool%26quot%3B%20feel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ELinen%20sheets%20vs.%20cotton%20%E2%80%94%20What's%20the%20difference%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ELewenhaupt%20says%20linen%20is%20typically%20more%20durable%20than%20cotton%20as%20the%20fibers%20have%20a%20longer%20and%20more%20open%20structure.%20This%20structure%20makes%20linen%20more%20absorbent%2C%20which%20is%20what%20gives%20them%20that%20cooling%20sensation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20linen%20sheets%20for%20hot%20sleepers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Bide%2C%20yes.%20He%20says%20that%20linen%20is%20known%20to%20be%20absorbent%2C%20hence%20its%20use%20for%20dish%20towels%20and%20old-fashioned%20handkerchiefs.%20You're%20unlikely%20to%20get%20that%20%26quot%3Bclammy%26quot%3B%20feeling%20from%20a%20linen%20sheet%2C%20making%20it%20a%20great%20option%20for%20hot%20sleepers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20linen%20sheets%20best%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20%26quot%3Bbest%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20sheets%2C%20as%20what%20you%20sleep%20on%20is%20largely%20a%20matter%20of%20personal%20preference.%20However%2C%20linen%20sheets%20tend%20to%20be%20durable%20and%20long-lasting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20quality%20linen%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ELinen%20made%20from%20Flax%20grown%20in%20France%20or%20Belgium%20is%20the%20highest%20quality%2C%20according%20to%20Lewenhaupt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20hotels%20use%20linen%20sheets%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20hotels%20use%20linen%20sheets%2C%20but%20most%20use%20high-quality%20cotton%20sheets%20in%20their%20bedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20you%20sleep%20better%20with%20linen%20sheets%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20scientific%20evidence%20that%20linen%20sheets%20help%20you%20sleep%20better%2C%20as%20the%20material%20you%20sleep%20best%20on%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20preference.%20But%20if%20you%20tend%20to%20sleep%20hot%2C%20the%20breathability%20of%20linen%20may%20be%20beneficial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-linen-sheets%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718140777000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65948b5f1c5c7b8c9a0d71e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-linen-sheets%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20love%20linen%20for%20its%20natural%20temperature-regulating%20properties%20and%20durability.%20The%20best%20linen%20sheets%20include%20soft%2C%20cooling%2C%20and%20all-season%20options.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Shannon%20Ullman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-linen-sheets%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20drops%20lawsuit%20against%20Sam%20Altman%20and%20OpenAI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%2