20entering%20your%20ears%2C%20your%20brain%20interprets%20the%20sound%20like%20a%20steady%20hiss.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20white%20isn't%20the%20only%20%26quot%3Bcolor%26quot%3B%20of%20sound.%20There's%20also%20pink%20noise%2C%20which%20is%20white%20noise%20with%20the%20higher%20frequencies%20somewhat%20muted.%20If%20you've%20ever%20peacefully%20fallen%20asleep%20to%20the%20sound%20of%20steady%20rain%2C%20you've%20enjoyed%20pink%20noise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrown%20noise%20is%20another%20popular%20variation%20of%20multi-frequency%20sound%2C%20which%20is%20basically%20pink%20noise%20with%20even%20more%20muting%20of%20high%20frequencies.%20Think%20waves%20crashing%20on%20the%20shoreline%20or%20the%20sound%20of%20high%20winds.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20sound%20machines%20incorporate%20several%20noise%20%26quot%3Bcolors%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20form%20of%20nature%20sounds%2C%20such%20as%20wind%2C%20waves%2C%20rain%2C%20or%20streams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20overall%5C%22%3EBest%20overall%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20%26quot%3Bsmart%26quot%3B%20sound%20machines%20on%20the%20market%2C%20we%20highly%20recommend%20a%20unit%20with%20analog%20controls.%20There's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7010281%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estrong%20evidence%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20restricting%20phone%20use%20before%20bed%20improves%20sleep%20quality%20and%20duration%C2%A0and%20reduces%20the%20time%20it%20takes%20to%20fall%20asleep.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sound%2BSleep%20High%20Fidelity%20Sound%20Machine%20has%20all%20analog%20and%20intuitive-to-use%20controls%2C%20but%20doesn't%20sacrifice%20high-tech%20features.%20The%20machine%20%26quot%3Blistens%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20ambient%20noise%20in%20your%20bedroom%20and%20then%20adjusts%20its%20volume%20as%20necessary%20to%20help%20protect%20your%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%2010%20basic%20sounds%20to%20choose%20from%3A%20fireplace%2C%20waterfall%2C%20white%20noise%2C%20meditation%2C%20brook%2C%20rainfall%2C%20train%2C%20city%2C%20meadow%2C%20and%20ocean.%20These%20aren't%20short%2C%20annoying%20loops%20or%20synthesized%20sounds.%20Naturally%20recorded%2C%20high-fidelity%20sounds%20are%20carefully%20mastered%20to%20relax%20you%20into%20sleep.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20add%20two%20additional%20levels%20of%20%26quot%3Brichness%26quot%3B%20to%20each%20of%20those%20basics.%20For%20example%2C%20%26quot%3Bocean%26quot%3B%20starts%20with%20the%20simple%20sound%20of%20water%20crashing%20against%20the%20shore.%20Two%20additional%20levels%20add%20in%20seagulls%2C%20barking%20seals%2C%20and%20even%20a%20fog%20horn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20bed%20partner%20doesn't%20want%20any%20sound%20at%20all%2C%20there's%20a%20headphone%20jack%20so%20you%20can%20enjoy%20the%20peaceful%20tones%20on%20your%20own.%20You%20can%20let%20the%20machine%20run%20all%20night%20or%20set%20the%20timer%20to%20shut%20off%20after%2030%2C%2060%2C%2090%2C%20or%20120%20minutes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20budget%5C%22%3EBest%20budget%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20straightforward%20device%20offers%20six%20sounds%3A%20summer%20night%2C%20white%20noise%2C%20rain%2C%20brook%2C%20ocean%2C%20and%20thunder.%20The%20sound%20quality%20is%20excellent%20and%20the%20loop%20is%20unobtrusive%2C%20so%20you%20won't%20feel%20like%20you're%20listening%20to%20a%20broken%20record.%20Priced%20at%20just%20over%20%2415%2C%20this%20is%20a%20great%20option%20if%20you%20want%20to%20try%20out%20a%20white%20noise%20machine%20without%20breaking%20the%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Big%20Red%20Rooster%20Sound%20Machine%20includes%20an%20AC%20adapter%2C%20or%20you%20can%20run%20it%20off%20batteries%20while%20traveling.%20If%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20let%20it%20run%20all%20night%20long%2C%20there%20are%20several%20timer%20options%20to%20turn%20the%20device%20off%20after%2015%2C%2030%2C%20or%2060%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20white%20noise%20only%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20white%20noise%20only%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20common%20use%20for%20white%20noise%20machines%20is%20outside%20office%20doors%20to%20mask%20the%20conversation%20happening%20within.%20In%20those%20cases%2C%20nature%20sounds%20would%20be%20distracting%20and%20out%20of%20place.%C2%A0If%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20sound%20machine%20that%20can%20drown%20out%20noise%20for%20privacy%20%E2%80%94%20or%20are%20simply%20a%20white%20noise%20purist%20%E2%80%94%20the%20LectroFan%20High%20Fidelity%20White%20Noise%20Machine%20is%20your%20best%20bet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20machine%20doesn't%20have%20any%20nature%20sounds%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20your%20selection%20is%20limited.%20This%20high-fidelity%20device%20has%2010%20levels%20of%20fan%20sounds%2C%20including%20everything%20from%20industrial%20to%20an%20oscillating%20fan.%20It's%20also%20got%2010%20levels%20of%20white%20noise%20ranging%20from%20pure%20white%20to%20pink%20and%20brown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20large%20top%20speaker%20produces%20excellent%20sound%20and%20does%20a%20great%20job%20of%20masking%20outside%20noise%2C%20including%20tough-to-sleep-through%20disrupters%20like%20snoring%20or%20barking%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20run%20the%20device%20all%20night%20long%20or%20set%20the%20timer%20in%20hour%20increments.%20The%20LectroFan%20High%20Fidelity%20White%20Noise%20Machine%20comes%20with%20a%20USB%20power%20cable%20and%20AC%20adapter%2C%20so%20you%20can%20power%20it%20up%20just%20about%20anywhere.%20It's%20available%20in%20black%20or%20white.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20travel%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20travel%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0Homedics%20SoundSleep%20White%20Noise%20Sound%20Machine%20plays%20six%20sounds%2C%20including%20steady%20white%20noise%2C%20summer%20night%2C%20ocean%2C%20thunder%2C%20brook%2C%20or%20rain.%20Instead%20of%20using%20a%20dial%2C%20it%20has%20buttons%20for%20each%20sound%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20this%20machine%20stand%20out%20is%20its%20small%20footprint%20and%20lightweight%2C%20which%20make%20it%20great%20for%20travel.%20It%20clocks%20in%20at%20just%208%20ounces%2C%20and%20can%20run%20either%20on%20AA%20batteries%20or%20plugged%20into%20a%20wall%20outlet%20for%20maximum%20versatility.%20Plus%2C%20priced%20at%20about%20%2420%2C%20it%20won't%20be%20the%20end%20of%20the%20world%20if%20you%20accidentally%20leave%20it%20behind%20in%20a%20hotel%20room.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20Reviews%20contributor%20Maria%20Yagoda%20uses%20this%20machine%20nightly%2C%20including%20on%20trips%20across%20the%20globe.%20She's%20found%20that%20even%20her%20noise-sensitive%20chihuahua%20sleeps%20better%20when%20the%20machine%20is%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20our%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhomedics-white-noise-machine-review%5C%22%3EHomedics%20White%20Noise%20Machine%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20babies%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20babies%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ability%20to%20create%20a%20calming%2C%20comfortable%20place%20for%20your%20baby%20or%20young%20child%2C%20even%20when%20you%20are%20away%20from%20home%2C%20is%20almost%20priceless.%20So%2C%20a%20%2420%20sound%20machine%20that%20can%20create%20a%20familiar%20and%20soothing%20environment%20just%20about%20anywhere%20is%20well%20worth%20the%20price.%20Not%20only%20is%20Myla%20the%20Monkey%20charming%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20easy%20to%20use%20and%20portable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20compact%20sound%20maker%20features%20a%20built-in%20rechargeable%20battery%20and%20a%20large%20hook%20so%20it%20can%20easily%20be%20hung%20on%20the%20stroller%2C%20the%20car%20seat%2C%20the%20crib%2C%20or%20anywhere%20else%20you%20need%20to%20create%20a%20sleep%20environment.%20Myla%20has%20five%20ambient%20sounds%20(white%20noise%2C%20stream%2C%20crickets%2C%20vacuum%20cleaner%2C%20and%20heartbeat)%20and%20five%20lullabies%20(Hush%20Little%20Baby%2C%20Brahms'%20Lullaby%2C%20Rock%20a%20Bye%20Baby%2C%20Twinkle%20Twinkle%20Little%20Star%2C%20and%20Minuet%20in%20G).%20It%20can%20either%20play%20continuously%20or%20on%20a%2060%20minute%20timer%3B%20there's%20no%20option%20for%20shorter%20timers%20or%20to%20play%20just%20one%20lullaby.%20You%20can%20also%20use%20Myla%20as%20a%20nightlight%3B%20its%20cheeks%20light%20up%20when%20you%20press%20its%20tummy%2C%20which%20is%20practical%20and%20adorable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMyla%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20charged%20with%20a%20USB%20cable%2C%20which%20can%20be%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20pain.%20If%20you%20want%20a%20soother%20with%20more%20options%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20plug%20into%20a%20wall%2C%20VTech%20also%20makes%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-70273-20%26h%3D2552bdc1e9259a03e4faad9ce1592bb98149ce93fd94b01c4895a7b7df3fa450%26postID%3D66686d9ee7e1e0003ff25156%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-white-noise-machine%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB01N9HP5QI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETommy%20the%20Turtle%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-70273-20%26h%3Dacca798a036aa731db907b80fa7ed26cf3adc80620a2c60d168423769b8ab15a%26postID%3D66686d9ee7e1e0003ff25156%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-white-noise-machine%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB01NCM7795%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWyatt%20the%20Whale%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20though%20neither%20is%20as%20portable%20as%20Myla.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20smart%5C%22%3EBest%20smart%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20largely%20recommend%20white%20noise%20machines%20with%20analog%20controls%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20cheaper%20and%20screen-free%2C%20which%20is%20ideal%20before%20bedtime.%20That%20said%2C%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20an%20all-in-one%20device%20that%20functions%20as%20a%20gentle%20alarm%20clock%20and%20a%20sound%20machine%2C%20the%20Hatch%20Restore%202%20is%20your%20best%20bet.%20It's%20also%20a%20good%20pick%20if%20you%20want%20more%20customizations%20than%20those%20offered%20by%20analog%20machines.%20Just%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20your%20unit%20will%20have%20to%20be%20connected%20to%20WiFi%20in%20order%20to%20function%2C%20and%20almost%20all%20controls%20are%20through%20a%20phone%20app.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Hatch%20Restore%20comes%20with%2021%20preprogrammed%20sleep%20sounds%2C%20plus%20many%20more%20curated%20music%20playlists%2C%20dreamscapes%2C%20guided%20rest%20exercises%2C%20and%20sleep%20stories%20available%20through%20the%20Hatch%2B%20subscription%20(which%20is%20optional%20but%20will%20cost%20%244.99%20a%20month%20after%20a%20free%2030-day%20trial).%20It%20has%20the%20most%20customizable%20timer%20of%20any%20product%20in%20this%20guide%2C%20with%20the%20option%20to%20set%20timers%20for%20anywhere%20between%201%20minute%20and%2023%20hours%20and%2059%20minutes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20standout%20feature%20of%20the%20Hatch%20Restore%202%20is%20the%20ability%20to%20wind%20down%20or%20wake%20up%20with%20a%20simulated%20sunset%20or%20sunrise.%20We%20also%20love%20its%20option%20to%20set%20multi-step%20sleep%20routines%20that%20include%20your%20personal%20sunset%2C%20meditations%2C%20reading%20time%2C%20and%20then%20white%20noise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERead%20more%20in%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-wake-up-light-alarm-clock%5C%22%3Ebest%20sunrise%20alarm%20clocks%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20white%20noise%20machine%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnalog%20controls%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC7010281%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESeveral%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC6618184%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudies%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20indicated%20that%20using%20your%20phone%20close%20to%20bedtime%20can%20negatively%20impact%20your%20sleep%2C%20increasing%20the%20time%20it%20takes%20to%20fall%20asleep%2C%20reducing%20sleep%20duration%2C%20and%20resulting%20in%20poorer%20overall%20sleep%20quality.%20We%20recommend%20looking%20for%20a%20white%20noise%20machine%20with%20analog%20controls%20rather%20than%20one%20reliant%20on%20a%20phone%20app.%20Analog%20machines%20can%20be%20turned%20on%2C%20adjusted%2C%20and%20turned%20the%20need%20to%20look%20at%20any%20screens%2C%20and%20are%20the%20best%20option%20if%20you're%20purchasing%20a%20sound%20machine%20to%20improve%20your%20sleep%20quality.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ENon-looping%20sound%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20you%20prefer%20to%20fall%20asleep%20to%20nature%20sounds%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20look%20for%20machines%20that%20play%20non-looping%20sounds.%20Hearing%20the%20same%20obvious%20noises%20several%20times%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20a%20distinct%20bird%20call%20or%20the%20same%20pattern%20of%20rain%20%E2%80%94%20can%20be%20distracting%20instead%20of%20relaxing.%20This%20isn't%20so%20much%20of%20an%20issue%20if%20you%20only%20listen%20to%20straight%20white%20noise%2C%20however.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPortability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Once%20you've%20grown%20accustomed%20to%20a%20sound%20machine%2C%20it%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20fathom%20falling%20asleep%20without%20it.%20Many%20of%20our%20picks%20for%20the%20best%20white%20noise%20machine%20are%20easy%20to%20travel%20with.%20If%20you%20anticipate%20taking%20your%20machine%20on%20the%20road%20with%20you%2C%20look%20for%20options%20with%20a%20small%20footprint%20that%20can%20be%20operated%20using%20multiple%20power%20so