nt-elections-may-weaken-climate-ambition-road-to-cop29-looks-tough%2Farticleshow%2F110919446.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Floss-of-greens-in-eu-parliament-elections-may-weaken-climate-ambition-road-to-cop29-looks-tough%2Famp_articleshow%2F110919446.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Floss-of-greens-in-eu-parliament-elections-may-weaken-climate-ambition-road-to-cop29-looks-tough%2Famp_articleshow%2F110919446.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Unbelievable%20That%20Police%20In%202%20States%20Can't%20Trace%20A%20Woman%3A%20High%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20pulled%20up%20the%20Maharashtra%20police%20for%20its%20%26quot%3Bsuperficial%26quot%3B%20probe%20in%20tracing%20a%20woman%20who%20went%20missing%20after%20she%20went%20to%20Rajasthan%20three%20months%20ago%2C%20leaving%20her%20baby%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20division%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Bharati%20Dangre%20and%20Manjusha%20Deshpande%20directed%20the%20superintendent%20of%20police%2C%20Kolhapur%2C%20to%20coordinate%20with%20his%20counterpart%20in%20Jalod%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20ensure%20that%20the%20woman%20is%20traced%20and%20produced%20in%20court%20on%20June%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20remarked%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bunbelievable%20that%20police%20machinery%20of%20two%20states%2C%20Maharashtra%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%20were%20unable%20to%20trace%20a%20woman%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20was%20hearing%20a%20habeas%20corpus%20(produce%20person%20in%20court)%20petition%20filed%20by%20the%20woman's%20husband%20from%20Kolhapur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20claimed%20that%20his%20wife%20was%20detained%20by%20her%20father%20as%20he%20disapproved%20of%20their%20inter-caste%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20plea%2C%20the%20couple%20tied%20the%20kno