20Lt%20General%20Upendra%20Dwivedi%20has%20also%20undergone%20courses%20at%20the%20DSSC%20Wellington%20and%20Army%20War%20College%2C%20Mhow.%20He%20was%20conferred%20'Distinguished%20Fellow'%20in%20the%20coveted%20NDC%20equivalent%20course%20at%20the%20US%20Army%20War%20College%20in%20Carlisle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20has%20an%20M%20Phil%20in%20Defence%20And%20Management%20Studies%20and%20two%20Master's%20Degrees%20in%20Strategic%20Studies%20and%20Military%20Science.%20He%20has%20also%20been%20decorated%20with%20three%20GOC-in-C%20Commendation%20Cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Pande%2C%20who%20was%20scheduled%20to%20retire%20at%20the%20end%20of%20May%2C%20was%20given%20a%20one-month%20extension%20of%20service.%20He%20was%20appointed%20the%20Army%20chief%20on%20April%2030%2C%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718129880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fjnsnd5go_lt-general-upendra-dwivedi_625x300_11_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flt-gen-upendra-dwivedi-has-been-named-the-new-chief-of-army-5869380%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20armies%20is%20set%20to%20get%20a%20new%20chief%20with%20the%20government%20announcing%20that%20Lt%20General%20Upendra%20Dwivedi%20will%20take%20over%20as%20the%20Chief%20of%20Army%20Staff%20from%20General%20Manoj%20C%20Pande%20on%20June%2030.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flt-gen-upendra-dwivedi-has-been-named-the-new-chief-of-army-5869380%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flt-gen-upendra-dwivedi-has-been-named-the-new-chief-of-army-5869380%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flt-gen-upendra-dwivedi-has-been-named-the-new-chief-of-army-5869380%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222%20Indians%2C%20Recruited%20By%20Russian%20Army%2C%20Killed%20In%20Ukraine%20Conflict%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20Indians%20who%20were%20recruited%20by%20the%20Russian%20Army%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Russia-%20Ukraine%20conflict.%20Confirming%20this%2C%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20said%20the%20government%20has%20taken%20up%20the%20issue%20with%20Russia%20and%20asked%20that%20recruitment%20of%20Indians%20in%20the%20Russian%20army%20be%20stopped%20immediately%20and%20all%20Indians%20currently%20with%20the%20Russian%20army%20be%20allowed%20to%20return.%20The%20ministry%20has%20also%20asked%20people%20to%20be%20cautious%20while%20taking%20up%20jobs%20in%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20and%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20Moscow%20have%20strongly%20taken%20up%20the%20matter%20with%20the%20Russian%20Ambassador%20in%20New%20Delhi%20and%20with%20Russian%20authorities%20in%20Moscow%20respectively%2C%20for%20early%20release%20and%20return%20of%20all%20Indian%20nationals%20who%20are%20with%20the%20Russian%20Army%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20statement%20from%20the%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20also%20demanded%20that%20there%20be%20a%20verified%20stop%20to%20any%20further%20recruitment%20of%20our%20nationals%20by%20the%20Russian%20Army.%20Such%20activities%20would%20not%20be%20in%20consonance%20with%20our%20partnership%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20after%20reports%20came%20in%20of%20several%20Indians%20dying%20in%20the%20war%20--%20lured%20to%20Russia%20with%20promises%20of%20jobs%20--%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20had%20said%20they%20were%20trying%20to%20get%20the%20men%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20an%20understanding%20that%20something%20like%2020-odd%20people%20are%20stuck%2C%20we%20are%20trying%20our%20level%20best%20for%20their%20early%20discharge%2C%26quot%3B%20Foreign%20Ministry%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20the%20ministry%20said%2010%20Indian%20nationals%20working%20as%20support%20staff%20with%20the%20Russian%20military%20have%20returned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20thousands%20of%20its%20soldiers%20died%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20Russia%20is%20said%20to%20have%20recruited%20people%20from%20southeast%20Asia%2C%20including%20India%20and%20Nepal%2C%20to%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20said%20around%20200%20Indian%20nationals%20have%20been%20recruited%20since%20last%20year%20to%20work%20as%20support%20with%20the%20Russian%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20Indians%20who%20had%20gone%20to%20Russia%20were%20lured%20through%20YouTube%20videos%20that%20promised%20lucrative%20salaries%20as%20%26quot%3Bhelpers%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Russian%20army.%20But%20some%20of%20the%20men%20had%20called%20home%2C%20saying%20they%20were%20given%20combat%20training%20and%20pushed%20to%20the%20front%20after%20they%20reached.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20arrested%20four%20people%20for%20their%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20the%20human%20trafficking%20network.%20One%20of%20them%20was%20a%20translator%20working%20on%20a%20contract%20with%20the%20Russian%20defence%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718129700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2Fklh77hv_kherson-reuters-_625x300_30_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-indians-recruited-by-russian-army-killed-in-ukraine-conflict-5869471%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20Indians%20who%20were%20recruited%20by%20the%20Russian%20Army%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Russia-%20Ukraine%20conflict.%20Confirming%20this%2C%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20said%20the%20government%20has%20taken%20up%20the%20issue%20with%20Russia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-indians-recruited-by-russian-army-k