ed%2C%20Tesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20had%20congratulated%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20said%20he%20was%20looking%20forward%20to%20his%20companies%20doing%20%26quot%3Bexciting%20work%26quot%3B%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCongratulations%20%40narendramodi%20on%20your%20victory%20in%20the%20world's%20largest%20democratic%20elections!%20Looking%20forward%20to%20my%20companies%20doing%20exciting%20work%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Musk%20had%20said%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20had%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BAppreciate%20your%20greetings%20%40elonmusk.%20The%20talented%20Indian%20youth%2C%20our%20demography%2C%20predictable%20policies%20and%20stable%20democratic%20polity%20will%20continue%20to%20provide%20the%20business%20environment%20for%20all%20our%20partners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETesla's%20entry%20into%20India%20has%20been%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20will%20it-won't%20affair.%20Mr%20Musk%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20founder%20of%20SpaceX%2C%20had%20met%20PM%20Modi%20in%20the%20US%20in%20June%20last%20year%20and%20described%20himself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bfan%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20confident%20Tesla%20will%20be%20in%20India%20and%20will%20do%20so%20as%20soon%20as%20humanly%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20had%20announced%20a%20new%20electric%20vehicle%20policy%20which%20would%20cut%20taxes%20by%20as%20much%20as%2085%20per%20cent%20on%20the%20import%20of%20a%20certain%20number%20of%20electric%20vehicles%20to%20%26quot%3Battract%20investments%20by%20reputed%20global%20manufacturers%26quot%3B%20like%20Tesla.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718123940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fngu5jijg_hd-kumaraswamy_625x300_11_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fis-tesla-coming-to-karnataka-what-minister-hd-kumaraswamy-said-5868876%22%2C%22summary%22%3A