d.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhdfc-bank-hikes-fixed-deposit-rates-by-20-bps-with-effect-from-june-10-124061101042_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20move%20comes%20even%20as%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20decided%20to%20keep%20the%20policy%20repo%20rate%20unchanged%20in%20the%20June%20review%20of%20monetary%20policy%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhdfc-bank-hikes-fixed-deposit-rates-by-20-bps-with-effect-from-june-10-124061101042_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhdfc-bank-hikes-fixed-deposit-rates-by-20-bps-with-effect-from-june-10-124061101042_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhdfc-bank-hikes-fixed-deposit-rates-by-20-bps-with-effect-from-june-10-124061101042_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biannual%20Admissions%20Will%20Improve%20Enrolment%20In%20India%3A%20UGC%20Chairman%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Findian-universities-can-now-offer-admissions-twice-a-year-ugc-5866106%5C%22%3EUGC%20Chairperson%20M%20Jagadesh%20Kumar%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20talked%20about%20the%20biannual%20admission%20process%20according%20to%20which%20admissions%20can%20either%20be%20offered%20in%20January-February%20or%20July-August%20from%20the%20new%20academic%20year.%C2%A0%C2%A0Mr%20Kumar%20explained%20that%20currently%2C%20higher%20education%20institutions%20admit%20students%20in%20one%20academic%20session%2C%20which%20starts%20in%20July-August%20and%20ends%20in%20May-June.%C2%A0Students%20who%20miss%20the%20admission%20process%20have%20to%20wait%20one%20full%20year%20to%20get%20admission%20in%20colleges.%20The%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20wanted%20to%20introduce%20a%20system%20where%20students%20do%20not%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20an%20entire%20year%20for%20securing%20admission%20in%20colleges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20option%20of%20the%20biannual%20admissions%2C%20the%20institutions%20can%20now%20admit%20students%20twice%20a%20year%20from%20the%202024-25%20academic%20session.%20The%20decision%20is%20aimed%20at%20providing%20more%20flexibility%20to%20Higher%20Education%20Institutions%20(HEIs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20said%2C%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20university%20body%20had%20tested%20the%20biannual%20admission%20process%20in%20Online%20and%20Open%20%26amp%3B%20Distance%20Learning%20modes.%20After%20UGC%20permitted%20two-cycle%20admissions%20for%20the%20ODL%20modes%2C%20there%20was%20a%20significant%20rise%20in%20the%20number%20of%20enrolments.%20A%20total%20of%2019%2C73%2C056%20students%20enrolled%20in%20July%202022%2C%20with%20an%20additional%204%2C28%2C854%20students%20in%20January%202023.%20The%20numbers%20showed%20that%20a%20second%20academic%20session%20in%20a%20year%20enabled%20nearly%20half%20a%20million%20students%20to%20join%20the%20degree%20programmes%20of%20their%20choice%20without%20waiting%20a%20full%20academic%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnswering%20if%20the%20decision%20was%20taken%20by%20keeping%20all%20the%20stakeholders%20on%20board%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20biannual%20admission%20system%20is%20a%20global%20practice%2C%20admissions%20are%20conducted%20twice%20a%20year%20in%20all%20global%20universities.%20Only%20in%20our%20country%2C%20it%20is%20done%20once%20a%20year.%20After%20seeing%20the%20response%20of%20the%20students%20in%20the%20online%20programme%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20provide%20a%20similar%20option%20to%20the%20universities%20that%20offer%20courses%20in%20physical%20mode%20also.%20So%20this%20is%20not%20a%20mandatory%20requirement%20for%20institutions%20to%20offer%20the%20courses%20biannually.%20Only%20those%20colleges%2C%20that%20have%20the%20required%20infrastructure%20and%20faculty%20members%2C%20can%20opt%20for%20this%20system.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20if%20the%20decision%20was%20aimed%20at%20aligning%20the%20education%20with%20the%20international%20standards%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20explained%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20national%20requirement%20to%20increase%20the%20Gross%20Enrollment%20Ratio%20(GER)%2C%20and%20is%20also%20a%20strong%20recommendation%20of%20the%20NEP%202020.%20So%20it%20is%20the%20social%20responsibility%20of%20higher%20educational%20institutions%20to%20increase%20students%20intake.%20If%20admissions%20are%20conducted%20twice%20in%20a%20year%20and%20if%20universities%20effectively%20utilise%20the%20available%20infrastructure%20and%20the%20teaching%20faculty%2C%20they%20can%20actually%20admit%20more%20students%20and%20help%20in%20improving%20the%20GER.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20asserted%20that%20since%20the%20move%20has%20been%20introduced%20as%20an%20option%20and%20not%20as%20a%20mandatory%20step%2C%20it%20is%20has%20not%20received%20any%20objection%20from%20any%20university.%20The%20universities%20will%20require%20some%20planning%20and%20time%20to%20decide%20on%20how%20they%20can%20implement%20this%20biannual%20system.%20Only%20those%20universities%20who%20are%20in%20position%20to%20offer%20can%20offer.%20They%20have%20six%20months%20time%20to%20plan%20and%20implement%20the%20biannual%20admission%20system%20as%20the%20next%20admission%20process%20will%20be%20held%20in%20January-February.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718118240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fc4i91m6_ugc_625x300_02_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fbiannual-admissions-will-improve-enrolment-in-india-ugc-chairman-to-ndtv-5868317%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20the%20option%20of%20the%20biannual%20admissions%2C%20the%20institutions%20can%20now%20admit%20students%20twice%20a%20year%20from%20the%202024-25%20academic%20session.%22%2C%2