Like%20many%20of%20us%2C%20Nikhil%20grew%20up%20surrounded%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F316563%2Ftamil-nadu-sustsainable-home-with-plastic-bottles-and-mud-chuzi-vinu-daniel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevalent%20use%20of%20plastic%20bottles.%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20an%20overnight%20realisation%2C%20but%20I%E2%80%99ve%20always%20been%20conscious%20of%20environmental%20issues%20for%20as%20long%20as%20I%20can%20recall.%20However%2C%20when%20it%20came%20to%20taking%20action%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20sense%20of%20purpose%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20often%20stumbled%20upon%20articles%20highlighting%20the%20escalating%20plastic%20waste%20crisis%20in%20the%20country.%20%E2%80%9CI%20became%20increasingly%20aware%20of%20the%20problem%2C%20and%20as%20an%20entrepreneur%2C%20I%20felt%20compelled%20to%20seek%20a%20solution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20asserts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Nikhil%20acknowledges%20that%20there%20are%20a%20few%20alternative%20options%20to%20plastic%2C%20he%20was%20determined%20to%20develop%20a%20product%20that%20resembled%20plastic%20in%20appearance%20and%20affordability%20but%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F279849%2Fsustainable-pune-startup-studio-alternatives-upcycles-old-shipping-container-houses%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenvironmentally%20friendly.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-7-1717580167.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bottles%20can%20decompose%20in%20180%20days.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-7-1717580167.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-7-1717580167-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-7-1717580167-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-7-1717580167-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fasan-cup-7-1717580167-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352144%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20bottles%20can%20decompose%20in%20180%20days.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20take%20a%20break%20from%20my%20previous%20startup%20and%20focus%20solely%20on%20finding%20the%20right%20alternative%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20So%2C%20in%202021%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20sell%20his%20startup%20and%20concentrate%20fully%20on%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20delved%20into%20reading%20about%20alternatives%20that%20were%20currently%20available%20in%20the%20country%20and%20around%20the%20world.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20alternatives%20like%20copper%2C%20bamboo%2C%20and%20various%20forms%20of%20wood%20that%20people%20are%20using%20instead%20of%20plastic.%20However%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20these%20alternatives%20have%20their%20own%20drawbacks%20%E2%80%94%20they%20are%20expensive%20for%20widespread%20use%20and%20tend%20to%20be%20heavyweight.%20These%20issues%20pose%20logistical%20challenges%20for%20manufacturers%20looking%20to%20use%20them%20in%20packaging%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20decided%20to%20look%20for%20alternatives%20that%20were%20lighter%20in%20weight%20and%20sturdier%20in%20nature.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFinding%20the%20right%20niche%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20he%20co-founded%20Greenevon%20Bio%20Bottles%20along%20with%20Chintan%20Prajapati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CChintan%20joined%20me%20midway%20through%20my%20research.%20While%20I%20was%20confident%20in%20my%20direction%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20concentrate%20solely%20on%20research%20and%20sought%20someone%20who%20could%20effectively%20market%20the%20product.%20Chintan%20was%20the%20perfect%20fit%20for%20this%20role%2C%20and%20our%20responsibilities%20are%20divided%20along%20similar%20lines%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitting%20across%20from%20me%2C%20holding%20a%20bottle%20that%20resembled%20a%20typical%20single-use%20plastic%20bottle%20%E2%80%94%20with%20the%20words%20%E2%80%98I%20am%20a%20bottle%20but%20I%20am%20not%20plastic%E2%80%99%20printed%20on%20it%20%E2%80%94%20Nikhil%20is%20confident%20that%20the%20bottle%20will%20decompose%20in%20nature%20within%20six%20months%20or%20180%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20tap%20the%20bottle%2C%20and%20it%20will%20sound%20like%20plastic%3B%20you%20can%20touch%20it%2C%20you%20can%20feel%20it%20%E2%80%94%20it%20looks%20identical.%20The%20only%20difference%20is%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340584%2Fkarnataka-suresh-maithili-bhoomi-agri-ventures-turns-areca-palm-leaf-into-vegan-leather%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20biodegradable%2C%20plant-based%2C%20and%20environmentally%20friendly%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20material%20and%20the%20manufacturing%20process%2C%20Nikhil%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20my%20research%2C%20I%20explored%20how%20plants%20could%20be%20utilised%20to%20create%20various%20materials.%20Just%20as%20plants%20can%20be%20used%20to%20make%20leather%2C%20I%20was%20investigating%20similar%20possibilities%20when%20I%20stumbled%20upon%20the%20remarkable%20properties%20of%20sugarcane.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%2012