20eatery%20that%20has%20stuck%20to%20one%20philosophy%3A%20home%20food%20is%20the%20best%20food.%20Minakshi%20Jhaveri%2C%20a%20single%20mother%20started%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F252694%2Fswati-snacks-minakshi-jhaveri-iconic-eatery-india-inspiring-single-mother-success-stories-authentic-homemade-food-chaat-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESwati%20Snacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20any%20prior%20business%20acumen%2C%20serving%20four%20items%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3Esev%20puri%2C%20bhel%20puri%2C%20ragda%20pattice%20and%20pani%20puri%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%94%20priced%20at%20four%20%3Cem%3Eaanas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20currency%20unit%20used%20in%20British%20India).%20But%20with%20this%20simple%20formula%2C%20she%20created%20history%20and%20a%20multi-crore%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20son%20Anand%20once%20shared%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20treated%20all%20her%20customers%20the%20way%20she%20would%20guests%20who%20visit%20our%20home.%20For%20a%20guest%2C%20who%20is%20equivalent%20to%20God%2C%20you%20will%20prepare%20the%20food%20with%20the%20best%20intentions%20and%20a%20positive%20attitude%2C%20which%20automatically%20reflects%20in%20the%20taste.%20While%20growing%20up%2C%20I%20watched%20her%20spend%20that%20extra%20hour%20just%20so%20she%20could%20inspect%20the%20ingredients%20multiple%20times%2C%20or%20even%20walk%20kilometres%20to%20procure%20fresh%20ingredients%20like%20coriander.%20That%20dedication%20and%20care%20is%20what%20we%20have%20inherited%20from%20her.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThanks%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMadhuriDixit%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40madhuridixit%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20introducing%20me%20to%20my%20very%20first%20Vada%20Pav%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20delicious!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FTh40jqAEGa%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FTh40jqAEGa%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Tim%20Cook%20(%40tim_cook)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftim_cook%2Fstatus%2F1647969544437399554%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2017%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20guest%20list%20has%20seen%20the%20likes%20of%20legendary%20painter%20M%20F%20Husain%20and%20%3Cem%3Etabla%3C%2Fem%3E%20maestro%20Zakir%20Hussain.%20In%20a%202020%20article%20by%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Michelin%20star%20chef%20Ravinder%20Bhogal%20of%20Jikoni%20in%20London%20hailed%20the%20eatery%20for%20its%20%3Cem%3Evada%20pav%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20recent%20addition%20to%20this%20list%20was%20Apple%20CEO%20Tim%20Cook%20who%20snacked%20on%20a%20%3Cem%3Evada%20pav%3C%2Fem%3E%20along%20with%20actress%20Madhuri%20Dixit%20while%20on%20his%20visit%20to%20Mumbai%20in%20April%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E8.%20Jai%20Maharashtra%20Vadapav%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fchef.saransh%252Fposts%252Fpfbid0N149N6gQ3eiHBExBBaaNeQtuUcRASDJ7yRNKSYcy9RrrGkPngVquyB6xqZP2LUPEl%26show_text%3Dtrue%26width%3D500%26is_preview%3Dtrue%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22250%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocated%20in%20Andheri%20West%2C%20the%20eatery%20serves%20no-nonsense%20%3Cem%3Evada%20pav%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20manages%20to%20hit%20it%20off%20with%20one%E2%80%99s%20taste%20buds%20almost%20instantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20celebrity%20chef%20Saransh%20Goila%20took%20to%20Facebook%20to%20share%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Cem%3Ealoo%20vada%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20seasoned%20perfectly%20with%20lots%20of%20coriander%20in%20it%20and%20is%20really%20crisp%20on%20the%20outside%20with%20a%20thick%20%3Cem%3Ebesan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(chickpea%20flour)%20coating%2C%20I%20suspect%20some%20rice%20flour%20in%20the%20batter!%20The%20%3Cem%3Epudina%20chutney%3C%2Fem%3E%20(mint-flavoured%20sauce)%20consistency%20kinda%20%3Cem%3Ethecha%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20the%20real%20star%20and%20adds%20a%20lovely%20kick%2C%20also%20the%20garlic%20%3Cem%3Echutney%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20on%20point.%20I%20gobbled%20down%20three%20of%20these%20and%20yet%20I%20want%20one%20more.%20Probably%20the%20best%20lunch%20you%20can%20buy%20in%20Rs%2015!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1717494416000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FClassic-Vada-Pav-1-1716555449.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D351102%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Vada%20pav'%2C%20the%20beloved%20Indian%20snack%2C%20never%20fails%20to%20evoke%20nostalgia%20and%20emotional%20connections.%20Mumbai%20boasts%20iconic%20spots%20like%20Aram%2C%20Ashok%20Vaidya%20Vada%20Pav%2C%20Swati%20Snacks%2C%20and%20more%2C%20each%20offering%20unique%20renditions%20of%20this%20culinary%20classic.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F351102%2Fbest-vada-pav-places-mumbai-ashok-vaidya-aram-shankar-gajanan-swati-snacks-jai-maharashtra-shivaji-park%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20Use%20Cardboard%20Boxes%20to%20Protect%20Your%20Plants%20From%20The%20Heat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20time%20you%20receive%20a%20package%2C%20what%20do%20you%20do%20with%20the%20cardboard%20waste%3F%20In%20India%2C%20households%2C%20itinerant%20waste%20merchants%2C%20and%20garbage%20collectors%20jointly%20recover%202.4%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS0921344915300082%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHouseholds%252C%2520i