%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20Vinati%20explains.%20Dotted%20with%20tea%20and%20pepper%20plantations%20at%20the%20time%2C%20the%20couple%20was%20responsible%20for%20adding%20to%20this%20lush%20vegetation%20with%20fruit%20trees%2C%20vegetable%20crops%2C%20cloves%2C%20coffee%20and%20other%20spices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20well%20aware%20that%20the%20economics%20of%20organic%20agriculture%20aren%E2%80%99t%20lucrative.%20The%20prices%20did%20not%20justify%20the%20efforts%20they%20were%20putting%20in.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20saw%20this%20as%20our%20chance%20to%20make%20the%20authorities%20wake%20up%20and%20realise%20the%20difficulties%20that%20organic%20farmers%20are%20facing%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fcoonoor-homestay-2-1716370122.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20variety%20of%20birds%20make%20their%20way%20to%20the%20homestay.%20These%20include%20the%20thrush%20(L)%20and%20the%20white-cheeked%20barbet%20(R)%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fcoonoor-homestay-2-1716370122.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fcoonoor-homestay-2-1716370122-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fcoonoor-homestay-2-1716370122-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fcoonoor-homestay-2-1716370122-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fcoonoor-homestay-2-1716370122-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-350731%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20variety%20of%20birds%20make%20their%20way%20to%20the%20homestay.%20These%20include%20the%20t